e%20running%20IELTS%20coaching%20centres%2C%20students%2C%20and%20their%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20India-Canada%20standoff%20may%20not%20be%20a%20subject%20of%20immediate%20concern%20to%20people%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%2C%20it%2C%20however%2C%20has%20been%20a%20routine%20conversation%20from%20the%20paddy%20fields%20in%20the%20villages%20to%20markets%20in%20the%20cities%20of%20Punjab.%20There%20is%20a%20sense%20of%20anxiety%20prevailing%20across%20several%20sections%20in%20Punjab%20if%20the%20crisis%20could%20affect%20those%20wanting%20to%20move%20to%20Canada%20for%20work%20and%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Touchstone%20Educationals%2C%20CANAM%2C%20Skybird%2C%20Times%20Academy%2C%20and%20many%20other%20famous%20IELTS%20coaching%20centres%20located%20at%20Jalandhar%E2%80%99s%20inter-state%20bus%20terminal%2C%20it%2C%20at%20least%2C%20appears%20that%20it%20has%20been%20business%20as%20usual.%20Even%20today%2C%20the%20lane%20opposite%20the%20bus%20stand%20remains%20flooded%20with%20students%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20with%20students%20from%20rural%20areas%20thronging%20the%20area%20to%20join%20one%20of%20the%20IELTS%20coaching%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26170821%2Faaa0c7c9-337b-46d0-bf0a-3042c07822bf.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26170821%2Faaa0c7c9-337b-46d0-bf0a-3042c07822bf.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26170821%2Faaa0c7c9-337b-46d0-bf0a-3042c07822bf-300x196.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26170821%2Faaa0c7c9-337b-46d0-bf0a-3042c07822bf-1024x670.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-676977%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22785%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20complex%20near%20Jalandhar%20bus%20stop%2C%20with%20name%20boards%20of%20IELTS%20coaching%20centres%20and%20immigration%20consultants.%20Photo%3A%20Kusum%20Arora.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlmost%20the%20entire%20area%20around%20the%20bus%20stand%2C%20from%20where%20buses%20ply%20to%20nearby%20villages%2C%20is%20filled%20with%20swanky%20consultancies%20offering%20immigration%20services%20to%20Canada%2C%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Australia%2C%20Germany%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20and%20the%20Middle%20east.%20There%20are%20also%20a%20number%20of%20IELTS%20coaching%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuch%20is%20the%20craze%20among%20the%20youth%20to%20reach%20Canada%20that%20wall-size%20billboards%20of%20IELTS%20coaching%20centers%20and%20visa%20consultancies%20can%20be%20spotted%20in%20almost%20every%20village%20in%20Punjab%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20a%20group%20of%20students%20at%20the%20Jalandhar%20bus%20stand%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20travel%20advisory.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20confused%20too.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20cannot%20stop%20taking%20IELTS%20coaching%20classes.%20It%20is%20a%20tricky%20situation.%20Canada%20has%20shaped%20the%20lives%20of%20our%20siblings%20and%20friends.%20For%20us%2C%20it%20is%20a%20sure%20shot%20way%20of%20excelling%20in%20life%20and%20earning%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sukhjot%20Singh%20and%20Avneet%20Kaur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20pertinent%20to%20mention%20here%20that%20the%20September%202023%20intake%20in%20Canada%20was%20already%20over%20and%20students%20have%20reached%20Canada.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20students%2C%20who%20are%20currently%20undertaking%20IELTS%20coaching%2C%20will%20be%20joining%20their%20colleges%20during%20the%20January%202024%20intake.%20Admissions%20in%20Canada%20are%20held%20in%20January%2C%20May%2C%20and%20September%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnxiety%20among%20students%20and%20parents%2C%20say%20education%20consultancies%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJalandhar-based%20education-cum-visa%20consultants%20Sandeep%20Singh%20and%20Parmeshwar%2C%20who%20run%20Golden%20Pillars%20Immigration%20and%20Consultants%2C%20said%20that%20there%20is%20uncertainty%20around%20what%20and%20how%20things%20will%20unfold.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20time%20being%2C%20we%20have%20put%20the%20files%20on%20hold.%20Not%20just%20the%20study%20visas%2C%20we%20are%20also%20not%20taking%20applications%20for%20tourist%20visas%20and%20skilled%20category%20visas%20for%20Canada.%20The%20number%20of%20inquiries%20from%20the%20applicants%20has%20increased%20in%20the%20past%20week.%20People%20are%20in%20dilemma%20and%20so%20are%20we%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20that%20recently%20when%20a%20woman%20came%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20tourist%20visa%2C%20they%20had%20told%20her%20to%20wait%20for%20some%20time%20instead%20of%20getting%20her%20file%20stuck%20in%20the%20process.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20IELTS%20coaching%20classes%20and%20tests%20are%20going%20on%20as%20usual.%20Students%20are%20concerned%20too%2C%20but%20they%20have%20three%20months%20to%20go%20till%20they%20apply%20for%20the%20January%202024%20intake.%20We%20are%20hopeful%20that%20this%20standoff%20wears%20off%2C%20and%20the%20situation%20will%20improve%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parmeshwar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20consultant%2C%20Lovedeep%20Sing%20from%20North%20Nation%20Consultancy%20at%20Dasuya%2C%20Hoshiarpur%20district%2C%20who%20has%20a%20tie-up%20with%20Oceanic%20Worldwide%20Services%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CEver%20since%20the%20India-Canada%20standoff%20has%20begun%2C%20we%20have%20been%20getting%20regular%20inquiries%20about%20whether%20it%20will%20affect%20the%20student%20visa%20services%20too.%20There%20are%20all%20kinds%20of%20rumors%20in%20the%20market%20and%20not%20just%20the%20students%20but%20their%20parents%20are%20confused%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20education%20consultant%20also%20said%20that%20the%20India-Canada%20standoff%20has%20put%20the%20future%20of%20around%20five%20lakh%20students%20across%20India%20at%20stake.%20%E2%80%9CAround%20five%20lakh%20student%20visa%20applications%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20applied.%20Even%20last%20year%2C%20the%20total%20number%20of%20study%20visa%20applications%20from%20India%20were%202.65%20lakh%20out%20of%20which%201.32%20lakh%20were%20from%20Punjab%20alone.%20That%20shows%20the%20volume%20of%20students%20moving%20to%20Canada%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELovedeep%20said%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20been%20just%20a%20week%20and%20things%20will%20become%20clearer%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20hopeful%20that%20this%20will%20be%20sorted%20out%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Ravi%20Sharad%2C%20who%20is%20the%20director%20of%20Times%20Academy%2C%20Jalandhar%2C%20said%20things%20are%20%E2%80%9Cnormal%E2%80%9D%20and%20students%20are%20preparing%20for%20the%20January%202024%20intake.%20His%20academy%20is%20famous%20among%20students%20for%20IELTS%2C%20TOEFL%20(Test%20of%20English%20as%20a%20Proficiency%20Language)%20and%20PTE%20(Pearson%20Test%20of%20English)%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLargely%2C%20the%20students%20are%20not%20very%20aware%20of%20the%20details%20of%20the%20ongoing%20row%20between%20India%20and%20Canada.%20Their%20focus%20is%20to%20clear%20the%20IELTS%20test%20and%20reach%20Canada.%20We%20are%20running%20IELTS%20coaching%20classes%20in%20three%20shifts%20in%20a%20day%20and%20there%20is%20no%20impact%20on%20our%20centers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAman%2C%20an%20employee%20from%20Jain%20Overseas%2C%20Jalandhar%2C%20which%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20most%20sought-after%20names%20for%20student%20visa%20applications%2C%20said%20that%20though%20the%20number%20of%20queries%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20India-Canada%20standoff%20has%20increased%20but%20it%20has%20not%20impacted%20the%20flow%20of%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20we%20are%20also%20keeping%20the%20students%20updated.%20As%20and%20when%20any%20development%20takes%20place%2C%20we%20will%20update%20them%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStudents%20hope%20for%20early%20resolution%20of%20India-Canada%20standoff%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IELTS%20exam%20is%20held%20twice%20a%20month%20on%20Saturdays.%20On%20September%2023%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20the%20scene%20was%20no%20different.%20Like%20earlier%2C%20leading%20hotels%2C%20banquet%20halls%2C%20and%20marriage%20halls%20were%20booked%20as%20test%20centres%2C%20and%20students%20came%20in%20large%20numbers%20to%20appear%20for%20both%20the%20Academic%20IELTS%2C%20mandatory%20for%20student%20visas%2C%20and%20General%20IELTS%20for%20work%20permits%20and%20Permanent%20Residency%20(PR).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20swanky%20marriage%20palace%2C%20where%20over%20500%20students%20had%20gathered%20for%20the%20IELTS%20exam%20on%20September%2023%2C%20a%20student%20Navpreet%20Kaur%2C%20who%20came%20to%20appear%20for%20the%20exam%20from%20Nawanshahr%20district%2C%20said%20that%20right%20now%20her%20only%20concern%20is%20to%20get%20a%20good%20score%20in%20the%20IELTS%20test%20and%20join%20a%20good%20college%20in%20Canada%20during%20the%20January%202024%20intake.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26171237%2FIMG_2883-1-1-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26171237%2FIMG_2883-1-1-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26171237%2FIMG_2883-1-1-1-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26171237%2FIMG_2883-1-1-1-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-676982%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EStaff%20preparing%20for%20the%20IELTS%20exam%20at%20a%20marriage%20palace%20situated%20on%20GT%20Road%20in%20Jalandhar%20on%20September%2023.%20Photo%3A%20Kusum%20Arora.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20aware%20of%20the%20India-Canada%20tensions%2C%20but%20it%20is%20my%20earnest%20prayers%20that%20things%20normalise%20soon.%20Initially%2C%20when%20the%20Indian%20government%20banned%20visas%20for%20Indians%20in%20Canada%2C%20we%20expected%20a%20similar%20reaction%20from%20Canada%20too.%20We%20are%20glad%20that%20despite%20this%20tension%2C%20Canada%20avoided%20any%20such%20action.%20Indian%20government%20should%20sort%20this%20matter%2C%20our%20future%20is%20at%20stake%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESukhjit%20Kaur%20from%20Kapurthala%20district%20also%20said%20that%20they%20were%20alarmed%20over%20the%20rumours%20following%20the%20India-Canada%20standoff.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20past%20one%20week%20was%20quite%20difficult%20for%20us.%20I%20was%20preparing%20for%20my%20IELTS%20test%20and%20suddenly%20this%20news%20came.%20We%20just%20pray%20that%20things%20become%20normal%20between%20both%20countries.%20There%20are%20hardly%20any%20jobs%20and%20future%20here%20in%20India.%20We%20should%20not%20be%20robbed%20of%20our%20only%20chance%20of%20excelling%20in%20life%20by%20going%20to%20Canada%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20all%20her%20friends%20and%20cousins%20who%20went%20to%20Canada%20got%20settled%20within%20five%20to%20six%20years%20of%20time%20which%20was%20not%20the%20case%20in%20India%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInternational%20students%20in%20Canada%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20CBC%20report%2C%20Canada%2