3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20Justice%20Dharam%20Chand%20Chaudhary%2C%20heading%20the%20Chandigarh%20bench%20of%20the%20AFT%2C%20was%20transferred%20to%20Kolkata%20on%20Monday%20(September%2025)%2C%20the%20local%20bar%20association%20called%20the%20transfer%20a%20direct%20assault%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cindependence%20of%20judiciary%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20AFT%20chairperson%20had%20transferred%20Justice%20Chaudhary%20citing%20%E2%80%9Cadministrative%20reasons%20in%20public%20interest%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0However%2C%20the%20Chandigarh%20AFT%20bar%20association%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20alleged%20that%20Justice%20Chaudhary%E2%80%99s%20transfer%20was%20a%20result%20of%20the%20strict%20orders%20passed%20by%20him%20against%20senior%20officials%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsking%20the%20CJI%20to%20cancel%20Chaudhary%E2%80%99s%20transfer%2C%20the%20letter%20alleged%20that%20it%20all%20started%20when%20Justice%20Chaudhary%20took%20a%20grim%20view%20of%20non-implementation%20of%20various%20orders%20passed%20by%20his%20bench%20in%20the%20year%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20repeated%20opportunities%20and%20non-adherence%20to%20submissions%20made%20on%20affidavit%2C%20he%20issued%20bailable%20warrants%20against%20senior%20MoD%20officials%20in%20contempt%2Fexecution%20applications%20in%20May%20this%20year%2C%20the%20letter%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20MoD%20officials%20then%20approached%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20high%20court%20but%20failed%20to%20get%20any%20relief%20and%20were%20instead%20directed%20to%20file%20a%20compliance%20report%20to%20the%20Chandigarh%20AFT%20bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20then%20stated%20that%20after%20losing%20the%20case%20in%20the%20high%20court%2C%20the%20MoD%20officials%20instead%20of%20implementing%20the%20high%20court%20orders%20moved%20an%20application%20for%20transfer%20of%20contempt%20cases%20from%20the%20Chandigarh%20bench%20to%20the%20chairperson%20AFT%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20letter%2C%20without%20issuing%20notice%2C%20the%20chairperson%20on%20the%20first%20date%20of%20hearing%20on%20September%2015%20transferred%20contempt%20cases%20from%20the%20Chandigarh%20bench%20to%20his%20own%20bench%2C%20despite%20the%20matter%20having%20been%20already%20adjudicated%20by%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%20on%20September%2025%2C%20the%20chairperson%20transferred%20Justice%20Chaudhary%2C%20who%20in%20the%20past%20served%20as%20acting%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20high%20court%2C%20giving%20him%20less%20than%2012%20hours%20to%20relinquish%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisturbing%20trend%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChandigarh%20AFT%20bar%20association%20president%20R.S.%20Panghal%20and%20secretary%20Ajay%20Sheoran%20said%20in%20their%20letter%20that%20the%20message%20behind%20Justice%20Chaudhary%E2%80%99s%20transfer%20is%20loud%20and%20clear%20%E2%80%93%20that%20if%20you%20pass%20orders%20for%20strict%20compliance%20of%20judgments%20against%20senior%20government%20functionaries%2C%20then%20this%20will%20be%20the%20result.%20Hence%20all%20AFT%20members%20should%20refrain%20from%20passing%20strict%20orders%20against%20senior%20MoD%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20stated%20that%20it%20was%20truly%20heartbreaking%20that%20after%20steps%20were%20taken%20to%20get%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20AFT%20executed%20which%20were%20lying%20unimplemented%20for%20years%2C%20the%20chairperson%20had%20first%20transferred%20the%20contempt%20proceedings%20from%20the%20Chandigarh%20bench%20to%20himself.%20He%20then%20also%20transferred%20the%20judicial%20member%20who%20was%20ensuring%20compliance%20and%20adherence%20to%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20that%2C%20the%20chairperson%20also%20transferred%20the%20execution%20proceedings%20pending%20in%20the%20other%20benches%20of%20the%20principal%20Bench%20to%20his%20own%20Bench%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20them%2C%20this%20brings%20to%20attention%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20AFT%20under%20the%20MoD%2C%20which%20reflects%20a%20total%20conflict%20of%20interest%20and%20is%20in%20contempt%20of%20the%20laws%20laid%20down%20by%20the%20constitution%20benches%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPanghal%20and%20Sheoran%20cited%20%3Cem%3EUOI%20Vs%20R%20Gandhi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2010)%C2%A0and%20%3Cem%3EMadras%20Bar%20Association%20Vs%20UOI%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2021)%20wherein%20it%20was%20held%20that%20the%20tribunal%20cannot%20be%20made%20to%20function%20under%20the%20parent%20ministries%20against%20which%20it%20has%20to%20pass%20orders%20and%20should%20be%20made%20to%20function%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Law%20and%20Justice%20or%20the%20National%20Tribunal%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20that%20the%20continued%20functioning%20of%20the%20AFT%20under%20the%20MoD%20is%20a%20contempt%20of%20the%20above%20two%20judgments%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20then%20asked%20the%20CJI%20to%20save%20the%20dignity%20of%20the%20institution%2C%20the%20majesty%20of%20law%20and%20judicial%20independence%2C%20and%20take%20strict%20action%20in%20the%20matter%20by%20treating%20this%20as%20a%20letter%20petition%20by%20quashing%20the%20transfer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20asked%20for%20removing%20the%20AFT%20immediately%20from%20the%20control%20of%20the%20MoD%20so%20that%20the%20confidence%20of%20litigants%20and%20the%20legal%20fraternity%20is%20not%20threatened.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBar%20in%20protest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBar%20president%20Panghal%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20in%20their%20general%20body%20meeting%20held%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20to%20abstain%20from%20work%20indefinitely%20to%20protest%20the%20transfer%20of%20Justice%20Chaudhary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20they%20will%20take%20all%20possible%20measures%20to%20revoke%20the%20transfer%20since%20it%20was%20not%20only%20arbitrary%20but%20an%20assault%20on%20judicial%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20independence%20of%20the%20AFT%20must%20be%20restored%20since%20it%20is%20an%20important%20judicial%20body%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20thousands%20of%20armed%20forces%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESecretary%20Ajay%20Sheoran%20said%20that%20Justice%20Chaudhary%E2%80%99s%20transfer%20order%20was%20illegal%20and%20done%20under%20pressure%20from%20the%20MoD.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20treatment%20of%20Justice%20Chaudhary%20was%20unacceptable.%20He%20was%20given%20less%20than%2012%20hours%20to%20relinquish%20charge.%20We%20are%20in%20protest%20mode%20until%20his%20transfer%20is%20revoked%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695723305000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26152240%2Fdownload-9.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fchandigarh-aft-heads-transfer-under-pressure-from-defence-ministry-triggers-protests%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Chandigarh%20Armed%20Forces%20Tribunal%20bar%20association%20has%20said%20Justice%20Dharam%20Chand%20Chaudhary's%20transfer%20is%20a%20direct%20assault%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cindependence%20of%20judiciary%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fchandigarh-aft-heads-transfer-under-pressure-from-defence-ministry-triggers-protests%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20slice%20of%20the%20Golden%20State%20Warriors%20could%20fetch%20%24700%20million%20as%20sellers%20look%20to%20offload%20part%20of%20the%20NBA%20team%2C%20report%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Apple%20exec%20Eddy%20Cue%20celebrating%20at%20a%20Golden%20State%20Warriors%20basketball%