3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Farvindsubraman%2Fstatus%2F1702486406549954902%2Fphoto%2F1%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1695803896680000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2__-jV6dseqcmFf_DKkX1l%5C%22%3Erecent%20column%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20former%20chief%20economic%20advisor%20Arvind%20Subramanian%20and%20Josh%20Felman%20provided%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Farvindsubraman%2Fstatus%2F1702486406549954902%2Fphoto%2F1%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Farvindsubraman%2Fstatus%2F1702486406549954902%2Fphoto%2F1%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1695803896680000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2__-jV6dseqcmFf_DKkX1l%5C%22%3Eassessment%20based%20on%20the%20recent%20GDP%20growth%20numbers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20argued%20for%20the%20need%20to%20look%20at%20the%20%E2%80%9Cproduction%20side%E2%80%9D%20of%20growth%20evaluation%20measurement%2C%20while%20studying%20for%20discrepancies%20observed%20between%20the%20nominal%20and%20real%20growth%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETheir%20analysis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Farvindsubraman%2Fstatus%2F1702486406549954902%2Fphoto%2F1%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Farvindsubraman%2Fstatus%2F1702486406549954902%2Fphoto%2F1%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1695803896680000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2__-jV6dseqcmFf_DKkX1l%5C%22%3Eshowed%20a%20divergence%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20the%20real%20growth%20numbers%20were%20positioned%20against%20the%20nominal%20numbers.%20The%20nominal%20figures%20track%20the%20real%20numbers%20until%20the%20first%20half%20of%20FY23%20but%20then%20decline%20by%20a%20whopping%2014%25%20over%20the%20past%20three%20quarters.%20They%20say%20that%20this%20is%20%E2%80%9Ca%20narrative%20of%20an%20economy%20which%20has%20decelerated%20sharply%20to%20very%20modest%20levels%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20finance%20ministry%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bqprime.com%2Feconomy-finance%2Ffinance-ministry-defends-its-gdp-growth-estimates%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bqprime.com%2Feconomy-finance%2Ffinance-ministry-defends-its-gdp-growth-estimates%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1695803896680000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3__Y7ukKZdxTYuDLfAxL46%5C%22%3Ewas%20quick%20to%20respond%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Justifying%20its%20methodology%20for%20calculating%20GDP%2C%20the%20ministry%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bqprime.com%2Feconomy-finance%2Ffinance-ministry-defends-its-gdp-growth-estimates%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bqprime.com%2Feconomy-finance%2Ffinance-ministry-defends-its-gdp-growth-estimates%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1695803896680000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3__Y7ukKZdxTYuDLfAxL46%5C%22%3Eargued%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20real%20GDP%20growth%20was%207.8%25%20year-on-year%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20FY24%2C%20based%20on%20income%20or%20production%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3Eexpenditure%3C%2Fem%3E%20approach%20of%20GDP%20measurement%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20lower%2C%20it%20said.%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20a%20balancing%20figure%E2%80%93statistical%20discrepancy%E2%80%93is%20added%20to%20the%20expenditure%20approach%20estimate.%20These%20discrepancies%20are%20both%20positive%20and%20negative.%20Over%20time%2C%20they%20wash%20out.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20(Indian)%20GDP%20fails%20to%20measure%20and%20account%20for%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202007%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fgovernment-gdp-statistics-obsession%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fgovernment-gdp-statistics-obsession%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1695803896680000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw39JbxOdKs2up-WQSxaCA1M%5C%22%3Eessay%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20author%20discussed%20some%20of%20the%20fundamental%20limitations%20of%20GDP%20as%20an%20indicator%20of%20growth%20in%20India%20and%20much%20of%20the%20developing%20world%2C%20where%20an%20unorganised%20and%20informal%20workforce%20obtains.%20It%20might%20be%20worth%20recalling%20some%20of%20those%20arguments%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20GDP%20measures%20the%20total%20monetary%20value%20of%20final%20goods%20and%20services%20produced%20within%20the%20domestic%20territory%20of%20the%20country%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time.%20While%20significant%20methodological%20advancements%20have%20been%20made%20in%20GDP%20accounting%20at%20both%20the%20national%20and%20global%20levels%2C%20one%20critical%20limitation%20of%20both%20GDP%20and%20GNP%20(Gross%20National%20Product)%20is%20that%20they%20only%20value%20outputs%20at%20market%20prices.%20In%20countries%20like%20India%2C%20most%20economic%20activities%20occur%20outside%20the%20market%20and%20the%20value%20of%20their%20outputs%20needs%20to%20be%20calculated.%20This%20is%20called%20the%20%E2%80%9Cimputed%E2%80%9D%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESubsistence%20farmers%20consume%20the%20food%20they%20produce%2C%20and%20economists%20often%20fail%20to%20estimate%20the%20quantity%20of%20produce%20and%20impute%20market%20values%20to%20it.%20For%20homeowners%2C%20economists%20usually%20fail%20to%20impute%20the%20value%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdwelling%20services%E2%80%9D%20involved%20(as%20if%20the%20house%20owners%20are%20paying%20the%20rents%20at%20market%20rates%20to%20themselves).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20all%20non-market%20transactions%20or%20output%20is%20missed%20out%20from%20the%20official%20GDP%20accounting%20process.%20Its%20value%20isn%E2%80%99t%20even%20imputed.%20Look%20at%20India%E2%80%99s%20massive%20informal%20sector%2C%20which%20was%20hit%20worst%20by%20demonetisation%2C%20the%20hurried%20implementation%20of%20the%20GST%20and%20the%20curfew-style%20lockdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20income%20measures%20like%20GNP%2C%20which%20accounts%20for%20the%20incomes%20of%20all%20residents%20of%20a%20country%2C%20fail%20to%20realistically%20represent%20the%20living%20standards%20of%20people.%20An%20optimal%20standard%20of%20living%20is%20vital%20for%20measuring%20developmental%20progress.%20However%2C%20with%20GDP%20and%20GNP%2C%20you%20can%20get%20a%20perspective%20on%20living%20standards%20only%20by%20accounting%20for%20total%20and%20average%20monetary%20income%20(as%20done%20by%20per%20capita%20income).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20we%20are%20rational%20as%20consumers%2C%20the%20existence%20of%20positional%20goods%20(a%20concept%20coined%20first%20by%20the%20economist%20Fred%20Hirsch%20and%20explained%20as%20a%20good%20which%20is%20only%20valued%20by%20the%20possessor%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20possessed%20by%20others)%20in%20any%20country%2C%20makes%20income%20an%20unreliable%20gauge%20of%20true%20living%20standard.%20Positional%20goods%20have%20value%20because%20only%20a%20small%20proportion%20of%20potential%20consumers%20can%20have%20them.%C2%A0This%20means%2C%20even%20if%20our%20income%20increases%20(with%20an%208%25%20GDP%20growth%20rate)%2C%20we%20may%20still%20be%20unable%20to%20acquire%20houses%20in%20prime%20locations%2C%20a%20good%20education%20or%20access%20to%20top%20jobs.%20This%20point%20is%20connected%20to%20explaining%20India%E2%80%99s%20slowing%20productivity%20rate%2C%20exacerbating%20the%20skill%20gap%20and%20worsening%20unemployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20the%20distribution%20of%20income%20amongst%20and%20within%20households%20or%20economic%20classes%20is%20not%20captured%20by%20GDP%20data.%20For%20most%20studies%20measuring%20and%20accounting%20for%20trends%20in%20income%20inequality%2C%20survey%20methods%20based%20on%20consumer%20spending%20and%20consumption%20behaviour%20are%20used%20and%20relied%20upon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFourth%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20limitations%20of%20GDP%20is%20that%20much%20of%20the%20work%20done%20by%20people%20today%20remains%20under-measured%20or%20largely%20unaccounted%20for.%20Despite%20an%20overwhelming%20emphasis%20on%20it%20across%20social%20sciences%2C%20the%20value%20of%20work%20%E2%80%93%20a%20definitive%20condition%20of%20humanity%20in%20most%20of%20our%20history%20%E2%80%93%20is%20sporadically%20covered%20by%20modern%20economics%20as%20a%20subject%20beyond%20the%20income%20it%20generates%20from%20the%20hours%20recorded%20at%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFifth%2C%20on%20inflation%2C%20as%20explained%20more%20recently%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20notoriously%20high%20retail%20price%20inflation%20has%20a%20number%20of%20additional%20causal%20factors%20(read%20the%20evidence%20on%20seller%E2%80%99s%20inflation%20in%20the%20fuel-price-anchored%20inflation%20level)%20that%20find%20little%20focus%20or%20explanation.%20This%20counter-intuitively%20impacts%20the%20possibility%20of%20correctly%20diagnosing%20%E2%80%98real%E2%80%99%20growth%20trends%20(which%20are%20inflation-adjusted).%20If%20inflation%20or%20deflation%20measurement%20itself%20lacks%20a%20robust%20causal%20mechanism%20for%20measurement%20and%20validation%2C%20growth%20trends%20will%20showcase%20divergences%20between%20their%20real%20and%20nominal%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMethods%20in%20mainstream%20growth%20economics%20also%20fail%20to%20incorporate%20the%20effect%20of%20some%20of%20the%20techno-capitalistic%20advancements%20made%20like%20the%20role%20of%20the%20internet%2C%20telecommunications%2C%20and%20so%20on%20in%20shaping%20the%20productive%20capabilities%20of%20people%20in%20modern%20economies%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20work%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20summation%2C%20most%20GDP%20calculations%20%E2%80%93%20much%20like%20most%20economic%20indicator-based%20analysis%20%E2%80%93%20work%20primarily%20on%20%E2%80%98estimates%E2%80%99%20made%20with%20%E2%80%98extrapolations%E2%80%99%20from%20growth-driving%20sectoral%20trends%20based%20on%20real-time%20trends.%20The%20real%20question%20is%20whether%20these%20%E2%80%98extrapolations%E2%80%99%20end%20up%20reflecting%20India%E2%80%99s%20actual%20economic%20situation%20during%20a%20period%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIntersectional%20mechanisms%20to%20validate%20growth%20figures%20require%20focus%20and%20empirical%20scrutiny%20that%20is%20independent%20from%20political%20and%20partisan%20bias.%20Such%20assessments%20with%20historical%20context%20and%20time-series%20validations%20may%20help%20the%20government%20to%20stop%20its%20obsessions%20with%20popularising%2Fjustifying%20short-term%20trends%20that%20may%20do%20little%20to%20clarify%20but%20may%20rather%20confuse%20more%20within%20its%20own%20ranks-and%20the%20critics%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDeepanshu%20Mohan%20is%20Professor%20of%20Economics%20and%20Director%2C%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%2C%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University.%20He%20is%20a%20Visiting%20Professor%20to%20the%20School%20of%20International%20Development%20and%20Global%20Studies%2C%20University%20of%20Ottawa%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20an%20Honorary%20Research%20Fellow%2C%20Birkbeck%20College%2C%20University%20of%20London%20this%20Fall.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695722458000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F05211159%2FGDP-PTI.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fthe-limitations-of-indias-obsession-with-short-term-gdp-growth-data%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Most%20GDP%20calculations%20work%20primarily%20on%20%E2%80%98estimates%E2%80%99%20made%20with%20%E2%80%98extrapolations%E2%80%99%20from%20growth-driving%20sectoral%20trends%20based%20on%20real-time%20trends.%20The%20real%20question%20is%20whether%20these%20%E2%80%98extrapolations%E2%80%99%20end%20up%20reflecting%20India%E2%80%99s%20actual%20economic%20situation%20during%20a%20period%20of%20time.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fthe-limitations-of-indias-obsession-with-short-term-gdp-growth-data%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Will%20Ganapath's%20teaser%20be%20pushed%20for%20Tiger%203%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695722269000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103958670%2Cimgsize-84720.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftiger-shroff-starrer-ganapath-teaser-to-be-pushed-for-salmans-tiger-3-heres-what-we-know%2Farticleshow%2F103958670.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103958670.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E'Tiger%203%E2%80%99s%20teaser%2C%20Jackky%20Bhagnani%20and%20Tiger%20Shroff%20along%20with%20Vikas%20Bahl%20are%20contemplating%20changing%20the%20date%20of%20their%20teaser%20launch.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftiger-shroff-starrer-ganapath-teaser-to-be-pushed-for-salmans-tiger-3-heres-what-we-know%2Farticleshow%2F103958670.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20Injured%20After%20JetBlue%20Flight%20Caught%20In%20%26quot%3BSevere%20Turbulence%26quot%3B%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEight%20passengers%20of%20a%20JetBlue%20flight%20from%20Ecuador%20to%20Fort%20Lauderdale%20in%20Florida%20were%20hospitalised%20after%20the%20plane%20was%20caught%20in%20a%20turbulence%20before%20landing%20int%20he%20US%20city%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ECBS%20News%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20Monday%20(September%2025)%20whe%20the%20plane%20was%20caught%20in%20an%20%26quot%3Babrupt%20and%20severe%20turbulence%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20JetBlue%20