mbardier%20CL30%20jet%2C%20flying%20from%20Dillant-Hopkins%20Airport%20in%20New%20Hampshire%20to%20Leesburg%20Executive%20Airport%20in%20Virginia%2C%20encountered%20severe%20turbulence%2C%20resulting%20the%20death%20of%20one%20passanger%2C%20said%20the%20%3Cem%3ECBS%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%20The%20flight%20had%20to%20divert%20to%20Bradley%20International%20Airport%20in%20Windsor%20Locks%2C%20Connecticut.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20incident%20in%20March%2C%20multiple%20individuals%20were%20hospitalised%20after%20a%20Lufthansa%20flight%20from%20Austin%20to%20Frankfurt%2C%20Germany%2C%20encountered%20turbulence%20and%20had%20to%20make%20an%20emergency%20landing%20at%20Dulles%20International%20Airport%20in%20Virginia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20approximately%2020%20passengers%20and%20crew%20members%20aboard%20a%20Condor%20flight%20from%20Frankfurt%20to%20Mauritius%20sustained%20injuries%20due%20to%20turbulence.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695721740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-10%2Fvn7ck2o8_jetblue-airways-twitter_625x300_23_October_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F8-injured-after-jetblue-flight-caught-in-severe-turbulence-report-4424863%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20month%20ago%2C%2011%20people%20were%20hospitalised%20after%20a%20Delta%20flight%20experienced%20severe%20turbulence%20while%20approaching%20Atlanta's%20Hartsfield-Jackson%20International%20Airport.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F8-injured-after-jetblue-flight-caught-in-severe-turbulence-report-4424863%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Matter%20of%20Concern%20if%20Household%20Savings%20Are%20Down%20and%20Liabilities%20Up%3A%20Former%20PMEAC%20Chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F14185439%2Fcoins-gebbaa9855_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EN%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eet%20household%20financial%20savings%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fhousehold-savings-fall-to-five-decade-low-in-fy23-debt-remains-sharply-elevated-report%5C%22%3Edropped%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20a%20multi-decade%20low%20of%205.1%25%20of%20the%20gross%20domestic%20product%20(GDP)%20in%202022-23.%20In%20addition%2C%20annual%20financial%20liabilities%20of%20households%20rose%20sharply%20by%205.8%25%20of%20GDP%20compared%20with%203.8%25%20in%20FY22.%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-serious-is-the-fall-in-household-savings%2Farticle67345771.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindu%20BusinessLine%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20from%202011-12%20to%202019-20%2C%20the%20financial%20savings%20of%20the%20household%20sector%20have%20moved%20in%20a%20narrow%20range%20of%207-8%25%20of%20Gross%20National%20Disposable%20Income%20(GNDI).%20In%202020-21%2C%20it%20touched%2011.3%25%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20period%3B%20however%2C%20that%20was%20a%20lone%20exception.%20In%202021-22%20the%20financial%20savings%20of%20household%20sector%20was%208.3%25%20of%20GDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20finance%20ministry%20has%20dismissed%20the%20%E2%80%98critical%20voices%E2%80%99%20on%20household%20savings%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fbusiness%2Fno-distress-says-finance-ministry-household-savings-down-because-people-are-buying-homes-vehicles%2Farticle67329711.ece%5C%22%3Earguing%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20households%20have%20started%20taking%20loans%20for%20real%20estate%20and%20vehicles%20which%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20%E2%80%98confidence%E2%80%99%2C%20not%20%E2%80%98distress%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20serious%20is%20the%20fall%20in%20household%20savings%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20this%20argument%2C%20note%20that%20the%20economy%E2%80%99s%20financial%20dynamics%20can%20be%20categorised%20into%20three%20main%20sectors%3A%20the%20household%20sector%2C%20the%20government%20sector%2C%20and%20the%20corporate%20business%20sector.%20Each%20of%20these%20sectors%20play%20a%20distinct%20role%20in%20the%20economy%E2%80%99s%20overall%20financial%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20household%20sector%2C%20by%20nature%20of%20saving%20more%20than%20it%20borrows%2C%20accumulates%20surplus%20savings%2C%20which%20can%20then%20be%20channeled%20into%20investments%2C%20lending%2C%20and%20capital%20formation.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20government%20and%20corporate%20business%20sectors%20often%20need%20to%20borrow%20to%20finance%20their%20activities%2C%20leading%20to%20deficits%20in%20their%20respective%20financial%20positions.%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20context%2C%20C.%20Rangarajan%2C%20former%20chairman%2C%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%2C%20and%20former%20RBI%20governor%20and%20D.K.%20Srivastava%2C%20former%20director%20and%20honorary%20professor%2C%20Madras%20School%20of%20Economics%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-serious-is-the-fall-in-household-savings%2Farticle67345771.ece%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reduction%20in%20the%20net%20financial%20assets%20rate%20is%20primarily%20due%20to%20a%20rise%20in%20financial%20liabilities.%20There%20can%20be%20many%20interpretations%20of%20this%20rise.%20An%20optimistic%20interpretation%20of%20this%20rise%20in%20the%20borrowings%20of%20household%20sector%20which%20also%20includes%20non-corporate%20businesses%20is%20that%20this%20sector%20is%20buoyant%20and%20has%20borrowed%20more.%20Nevertheless%2C%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20net%20financial%20savings%20ratio%20of%20the%20sector%20has%20come%20down.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20is%2C%20the%20transferable%20savings%20ratio%20of%20the%20economy%20has%20come%20down%20and%20this%20will%20affect%20the%20borrowing%20programme%20of%20government%20and%20corporate%20sector.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20household%20financial%20assets%20include%20bank%20deposits%2C%20cash%20and%20equity%20investments%2C%20after%20deducting%20debt%20servicing%20and%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20government%20relies%20on%20these%20savings%20to%20fund%20its%20capital%20investments%20in%20physical%20assets%20like%20infrastructure%2C%20machinery%2C%20and%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20explain%20the%20problems%20the%20economy%20will%20face%20due%20to%20low%20household%20savings%2C%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20rule%20that%20the%20acceptable%20level%20of%20fiscal%20deficit%20of%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20States%20taken%20together%20can%20be%206%25%20of%20the%20GDP%20is%20based%20on%20the%20assumption%20that%20household%20savings%20will%20be%20around%207%25%20of%20GDP%20and%20the%20net%20inflow%20of%20resources%20from%20abroad%20will%20be%20around%202.5%25%20of%20GDP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20gives%20a%20borrowing%20space%20of%209.5%25%20of%20GDP.%20This%20borrowing%20space%20could%20be%20shared%20by%20the%20government%20to%20the%20extent%20of%206%25%20of%20GDP%2C%20and%20by%20the%20public%20sector%20enterprises%20to%20the%20extent%20of%201%20to%201.5%25%20of%20GDP.%20The%20remaining%20borrowing%20space%20of%202%20to%202.5%25%20is%20left%20for%20the%20private%20corporate%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%E2%80%9Cif%20the%20savings%20rate%20of%20the%20household%20sector%20fell%20to%205%25%20of%20GDP%20permanently%2C%20we%20cannot%20have%20the%206%25%20rule.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20say%20the%20fiscal%20deficit%20will%20have%20to%20be%20lower.%20And%20this%20situation%20will%20put%20the%20budgets%20under%20a%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20further%20note%20that%20if%20financial%20liabilities%20are%20to%20rise%2C%20gross%20financial%20assets%20of%20household%20sector%20should%20go%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20direct%20way%20to%20calculate%20savings%2C%20but%20if%20at%20the%20end%20of%20computations%2C%20the%20estimate%20is%20that%20savings%20are%20down%2C%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%2C%20they%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20concern%20was%20also%20echoed%20by%20Saugata%20Bhattacharya%20economist%20at%20Axis%20Bank%20Ltd.%20He%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Findicators%2Ffalling-household-savings-a-risk-to-indias-world-beating-growth%2Farticleshow%2F103925983.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CHousehold%20financial%20savings%20not%20keeping%20pace%20with%20growth%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern.%20Without%20adequate%20domestic%20savings%2C%20funding%20the%20needed%20investment%20will%20require%20large%20foreign%20capital%2C%20which%20is%20often%20volatile.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20achieve%20India%E2%80%99s%20projected%20GDP%20growth%20of%206.1%25%20in%20the%20current%20fiscal%20year%20ending%20March%2C%20the%20government%20needs%20to%20sustain%20investment%20spending%2C%20and%20not%20just%20rely%20on%20private%20consumption%20fueled%20by%20debt%20as%20an%20engine%20of%20growth%2C%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20observed%20that%20the%20rise%20in%20financial%20liabilities%20with%20falling%20assets%20levels%20could%20be%20a%20sign%20of%20rising%20inequality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20household%20sector%20is%20consuming%20by%20borrowing%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rupa%20Rege%20Nitsure%20economist%20with%20L%26amp%3BT%20Finance%20Holdings%20Ltd%20told%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20happens%20when%20income%20level%20stays%20stagnant%20but%20inflation%20creeps%20up.%20The%20recovery%20is%20not%20broad-based%20%E2%80%94%20while%20a%20section%20splurges%20on%20luxury%20goods%2C%20others%20are%20borrowing%20to%20stay%20afloat.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695721521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F14185439%2Fcoins-gebbaa9855_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fa-matter-of-concern-if-household-savings-are-down-and-liabilities-up-former-pmeac-chief%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20order%20to%20achive%20India's%20projected%20GDP%20growth%20of%206.1%25%20in%20the%20current%20fiscal%20year%20ending%20in%20March%2C%20the%20government%20must%20maintain%20its%20investment%20spending%20rather%20than%20depending%20solely%20on%20growth%20driven%20by%20private%20consumption%20fueled%20by%20debt.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fa-matter-of-concern-if-household-savings-are-down-and-liabilities-up-former-pmeac-chief%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Shilpa%20was%20snubbed%20by%20THIS%20actor's%20security%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695721492000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103958303%2Cimgsize-24684.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwhen-shilpa-shetty-was-pushed-by-arnold-schwarzeneggers-security-husband-raj-kundra-lost-his-cool%2Farticleshow%2F103958404.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103958404.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EShilpa%20Shetty%20reveals%20that%20she%20never%20turns%20down%20her%20fans%20for%20photos%20as%20she%20was%20once%20denied%20a%20photo%20with%20Arnold%20Schwarzenegger%20by%20his%20security%20and%20she%20was%20disheartened.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwhen-shilpa-shetty-was-pushed-by-arnold-schwarzeneggers-security-husband-raj-kundra-lost-his-cool%2Farticleshow%2F103958404.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Steve%20Coogan%20Boards%20Stanley%20Kubrick%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Dr.%20Strangelove%E2%80%99%20London%20Stage%20Adaptation%20From%20%E2%80%98Veep%E2%80%99%20Creator%20Armando%20Iannucci%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695721170000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FStrangelove-Steve-Coogan.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235735306%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22British%20actor%20and%20comedian%20Steve%20Coogan%20is%20all%20set%20to%20channel%20his%20inner%20Peter%20Sellers.%20The%20%E2%80%9CAlan%20Partridge%E2%80%9D%20star%20will%20play%20multiple%20roles%20as%20the%20lead%20in%20the%20London%20stage%20version%20of%20Stanley%20Kubrick%E2%80%99s%201964%20political%20satire%20film%20%E2%80%9CDr.%20Strangelove%C2%A0or%3A%20How%20I%20Learned%20to%20Stop%20Worrying%20and%20Love%20the%20Bomb%2C%E2%80%9D%20being%20adapted%20by%20%E2%80%9CVeep%E2%80%9D%20creator%C2%A0Armando%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Flegit%2Fglobal%2Fsteve-coogan-stanley-kubrick-dr-strangelove-veep-armando-iannucci-1235735306%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Flegit%2Fglobal%2Fsteve-coogan-stanley-kubrick-dr-strangelove-veep-armando-iannucci-1235735306%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Flegit%2Fglobal%2Fsteve-coogan-stanley-kubrick-dr-strangelove-veep-armando-iannucci-1235735306%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Won't%20be%20quiet%20on%20next%20date'%3A%20SC%20on%20delay%20in%20appointment%20of%20judges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695721136000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103958070%2Cimgsize-142722.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fi-will-not-be-quiet-on-next-date-sc-seeks-centres-response-on-delay-in-clearing-names-for-appointment-of-judges%2Farticleshow%2F103957983.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20has%20expressed%20its%20dismay%20with%20the%20delay%20by%20the%20Centre%20in%20clearing%2070%20names%20for%20judgeship%20recommended%20by%20various%20high%20courts.%20The%20attorney%20general%20sought%20a%20week's%20time%20to%20respond.%20The%20court%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20take%20up%20the%20case%20every%2010-12%20days.%20The%20case%20was%20filed%20by%20Advocates%20Association%20of%20Bengaluru%2C%20seeking%20contempt%20action%20against%20the%20ministry%20of%20law%20and%20justice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pushed%20to%20the%20Limit%3A%20Poor%2C%20Stressful%20Work%20Conditions%20Mar%20Freight%20Train%20Drivers'%20Lives%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25132053%2F288A2183.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOn%20June%202%20%2C%202023%20288%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20railway%20crash%20near%20Bahanaga%20Bazaar%20Railway%20Station%20in%20Odisha%2C%20making%20this%20India%E2%80%99s%20worst%20train%20accident%20since%201995.%20The%20discussion%20on%20railway%20safety%20this%20has%20provoked%20has%20largely%20ignored%20the%20working%20conditions%20of%20railway%20workers%2C%20perhaps%20the%20largest%20public-sector%20workforce%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20following%20two%20articles%20consider%20the%20working%20conditions%20of%20railway%20train%20drivers%2C%20known%20in%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20as%20%E2%80%98loco%20pilots%E2%80%99%20(LPs)%2C%20particularly%20freight%20or%20goods%20LPs%20who%20constitute%20roughly%2070%25%20of%20the%20total%20LPs%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20information%20for%20these%20articles%20was%20collected%20through%20interviews%20with%20members%20of%20the%20Loco%20Running%20Staff%20Association%20(LRSA)%2C%20a%20trade%20union%20of%20approximately%2044%2C000%20railway%20running%20staff.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20the%20first%20article%20here%2C%20on%20LPs%E2%80%99%20working%20hours%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fpushed-to-the-limit-the-working-lives-of-indias-freight-train-drivers%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20second%20article%20looks%20at%20LPs%E2%80%99%20working%20conditions%2C%20the%20intensification%20of%20work%20and%20the%20poor%20condition%20of%20railway%20infrastructure%20and%20how%20this%20results%20in%20higher%20stress%20levels%20for%20LPs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20intensification%20of%20LPs%E2%80%99%20work%20is%20not%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20the%20extension%20of%20working%20hours.%20The%20addition%20of%20duties%20in%20an%20increasingly%20poorly%20maintained%20railway%20system%20makes%20their%20work%20increasingly%20stressful%20and%20dangerous.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20can%20observe%20this%20at%20every%20step%20of%20an%20LP%E2%80%99s%20shift%2C%20which%20includes%20two%20components%3A%20a%20%E2%80%9Crunning%20time%E2%80%9D%2C%20when%20the%20train%20is%20being%20driven%2C%20and%20a%20period%20for%20preparatory%20and%20complementary%20work%20before%20and%20after%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPreparatory%20work%20consists%20of%20handing%20over%20and%20taking%20charge%20of%20the%20train%2C%20reading%20the%20route%E2%80%99s%20caution%20orders%20(for%20instance%2C%20where%20on%20the%20route%20the%20train%20should%20be%20driven%20at%20a%20slower%20speed%2C%20where%20faults%20have%20been%20reported%20on%20the%20tracks%20etc.)%20and%20undergoing%20a%20breathalyser%20test.%20Then%20the%20LP%20must%20prepare%2C%20check%20and%20activate%20the%20engines%3B%20check%20the%20breaks%20through%20a%20break-fail%20test%3B%20check%20the%20lights%20and%20oiling%3B%20and%20check%20that%20the%20logbook%20of%20defects%20has%20been%20attended%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20is%20here%20that%20the%20problems%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20goods%20trains%20are%20longer%20(with%20sometimes%2068%20wagons%2C%20at%20a%20length%20of%20up%20to%203.5%20km)%2C%20have%20an%20increased%20freight%20load%20(from%201%2C600%20tonnes%2020%20years%20earlier%2C%20to%206%2C000%20tonnes%20today)%20and%20must%20be%20run%20faster%20(from%20an%20earlier%20speed%20of%2040%20km%2Fhr-85%20km%2Fhr%20to%2090-100%20km%2Fhr%20or%20120-160%20km%2Fhr%20in%20the%20case%20of%20super-fast%20trains)%20from%20what%20they%20were%20earlier.%20Clearly%2C%20train%20marshalling%2C%20the%20goods%20load%20and%20maintenance%20of%20rolling%20stock%20must%20be%20paid%20close%20attention%20to%2C%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20train.%20Yet%2C%20LRSA%20members%20claim%20it%20is%20precisely%20these%20processes%20which%20have%20been%20undermined%20by%20sub-contracting%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELPs%20claim%20that%20since%20train%20marshalling%20has%20been%20sub-contracted%2C%20train%20formation%20rules%20are%20being%20flaunted%2C%20which%20increases%20the%20chances%20of%20derailment.%20For%20instance%2C%20goods%20trains%20must%20have%20some%20empty%20wagons%20placed%20between%20loaded%20wagons%2C%20which%20can%20relieve%20some%20of%20the%20shock%20of%20a%20break%20on%20the%20loaded%20wagons.%20However%2C%20these%20empty%20wagons%20are%20not%20being%20coupled%20to%20trains%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20possibility%20of%20loaded%20wagons%20lifting%20if%20the%20LP%20has%20to%20break%20at%20speed%2C%20possibly%20derailing%20or%20even%20capsizing%20the%20train.%20Moreover%2C%20LPs%20claim%20contractors%20frequently%20load%20goods%20trains%20with%20coal%2C%20iron%20ore%20etc.%20beyond%20the%20maximum%20markings%20on%20railway%20wagons%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20axle%20breakage%20and%20the%20breaking%20of%20trains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20LPs%20claim%20that%20the%20sub-contracting%20of%20the%20work%20of%20the%20Carriage%20and%20Wagon%20departments%20in%20loco%20sheds%20has%20led%20to%20compromises%20in%20the%20maintenance%20of%20rolling%20stock.%20While%20earlier%20a%20train%20was%20checked%20at%20a%20Carriage%20and%20Wagon%20depot%20every%20400%20km%2C%20trains%20now%20often%20run%20long%20routes%2C%20such%20as%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20Kolkata%2C%20without%20a%20single%20check.%20Sometimes%20trains%20run%20more%20than%20one%20trip%20without%20being%20checked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20context%20of%20falling%20safety%20standards%2C%20much%20of%20the%20work%20of%20checking%20of%20trains%20before%20departure%20has%20been%20put%20onto%20the%20shoulders%20of%20LPs%20and%20guards%20%E2%80%93%20a%20technical%20task%20they%20are%20not%20trained%20to%20do.%20For%20instance%2C%20LPs%20are%20required%20to%20check%20the%20train%E2%80%99s%20axle%20and%20the%20goods%20load%20that%20they%20are%20carrying.%20But%20neither%20LPs%20nor%20guards%20have%20any%20formal%20training%20in%20this%20department%2C%20and%20argue%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20properly%20check%20whether%20the%20goods%20have%20been%20loaded%20safely.%20And%20when%20an%20LP%20does%20notice%20a%20defect%20and%20draws%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20chargeman%20to%20it%2C%20LPs%20claim%20that%2C%20especially%20on%20night%20shifts%2C%20sometimes%20there%20simply%20aren%E2%80%99t%20maintenance%20workers%20to%20rectify%20the%20issues%20due%20to%20staff%20vacancies.%20Similarly%2C%20when%20LPs%20report%20errors%20on%20the%20track%2C%20they%20are%20not%20attended%20to%20%E2%80%93%20in%20some%20instances%2C%20these%20are%20errors%20which%20have%20caused%20derailments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20377px)%2085vw%2C%20377px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25153305%2F288A2342.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22377%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25153305%2F288A2342.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25153305%2F288A2342-200x300.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25153305%2F288A2342-683x1024.jpg%20683w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-676771%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22566%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAll%20India%20Loco%20Running%20Staff%20Association%E2%80%99s%20meeting%20of%20around%20500%20running%20staff%20near%20Jantar%20Mantar%20protesting%20against%20the%20monetisation%20of%20the%20Railways%20and%20to%20seek%20remedies%20to%20the%20grievances%20faced%20by%20running%20staff.%20Photo%3A%20Zaen%20Alkazi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20slackening%20of%20safety%20standards%20and%20procedures%20due%20to%20subcontracting%20results%20in%20increased%20stress%20to%20the%20LP%E2%80%99s%20heart.%20Sometimes%20a%20signal%20accidentally%20bobs%20when%20being%20cleaned%2C%20and%20the%20train%20going%20at%20100%20km%2Fhour%20must%20be%20suddenly%20stopped%20which%20seriously%20affects%20the%20LP%E2%80%99s%20heart%20rate.%20Similarly%2C%20while%20railway%20procedure%20requires%20that%20two%20stops%20at%20distances%20of%20600%20m%20and%20beyond%20that%20a%20red-flag%20man%20at%2045%20m%20should%20signal%20to%20LPs%20to%20stop%20when%20electric%20wire%20maintenance%20is%20taking%20place%2C%20private%20contractors%20only%20station%20one%20red-flag%20man.%20LPs%20claim%20that%20this%20is%20insufficient%20warning%20to%20stop%20a%20train%20going%20at%20100%20km%2Fhour%2C%20and%20that%20this%20has%20already%20led%20to%20cases%20of%20maintenance%20workers%20getting%20hurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20one%20exasperated%20LP%20put%20it%20to%20me%20after%20describing%20the%20state%20of%20safety%20in%20the%20Railways%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESab%20bhagwan-bharose%20chal%20raha%20hai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Everything%20has%20been%20left%20at%20god%E2%80%99s%20mercy).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20extreme%20working%20environment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20part%20of%20the%20LP%E2%80%99s%20shift%2C%20the%20running%20time%2C%20consists%20of%20starting%20the%20train%2C%20exchanging%20the%20green%20signal%20with%20the%20guard%20and%20station%20master%2C%20and%20piloting%20the%20engine.%20During%20running%2C%20the%20LP%20needs%20to%20control%20the%20speed%20of%20the%20train%20in%20line%20with%20regulations%20and%20the%20caution%20orders%20for%20the%20section%2C%20constantly%20check%20the%20overhead%20electrical%20wire%20to%20see%20that%20no%20part%20of%20it%20is%20hanging%20and%20check%20the%20air%20pressure%20and%20break%20power.%20The%20LP%20also%20needs%20to%20watch%20for%20animals%20and%20human%20beings%20trespassing%20on%20the%20track.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20LRSA%20officials%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faifap.org.in%2F10136%2F%5C%22%3Eclaim%3C%2Fa%3E%20goods%20LPs%20are%20increasingly%20being%20forced%20to%20take%20on%20extra%20duties%20%E2%80%93%20for%20instance%2C%20working%20multiple%20trains%20in%20one%20spell%20of%20duty%20and%20being%20made%20to%20stop%20at%20stations%20and%20shunt%20other%20trains%20before%20picking%20up%20their%20journey%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20running%2C%20the%20conditions%20of%20the%20loco%20cab%20have%20made%20loco%20piloting%20a%20stressful%20and%20dangerous%20job.%20For%20there%20are%20fundamental%20problems%20with%20the%20design%20of%20the%20loco%20cabs%20where%20LPs%20must%20spend%20most%20of%20their%20working%20lives.%20There%20is%20no%20air%20temperature%20regulation%20within%20the%20cab%2C%20where%20temperatures%20rise%20to%20over%2060%C2%B0C%20in%20summer%20and%20drop%20to%20near%20zero%20in%20winter%2C%20with%20wind%20entering%20through%20crevices%20in%20doors%20and%20windows.%20There%20are%20no%20toilets%20in%20most%20locomotives%2C%20an%20aspect%20of%20railway%20%E2%80%98design%E2%80%99%20that%20has%20remained%20unchanged%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20Indian%20railways%20in%20the%201850s.%20There%20is%20no%20proper%20sound%20proofing%20of%20the%20cab%2C%20where%20noise%20levels%20reach%20as%20high%20as%2098.4%20decibels%2C%20when%20the%20Occupational%20Safety%20and%20Health%20Administration%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Department%20of%20Labour%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.osha.gov%2Fnoise%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWith%2520noise%252C%2520OSHA%2527s%2520permissible%2520exposure%2Cdose%2520is%2520cut%2520in%2520half.%5C%22%3Eclaims%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20regular%20exposure%20to%20over%2085%20decibels%20for%20eight%20hours%20a%20day%20increases%20the%20chances%20of%20hearing%20loss.%20At%20times%20of%20reduced%20visibility%2C%20for%20instance%20during%20the%20North%20Indian%20winter%20smog%20and%20mist%2C%20LPs%20must%20keep%20blowing%20the%20train%20horn%2C%20which%20increases%20the%20noise%20in%20the%20cab%20even%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELPs%E2%80%99%20seats%20are%20uncomfortable%20and%20too%20far%20from%20the%20work%20panel%2C%20which%20forces%20them%20to%20constantly%20lean%20over%20or%20keep%20standing%20through%20the%20trip.%20An%20article%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fthe-nation%2Farticle30167487.ece%3Fart%3Dpackage%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFrontline%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20claimed%20that%20the%20cushioned%20seats%20and%20air%20conditioning%20in%20imported%20wagons%20are%20deliberately%20%3Cem%3Eremoved%3C%2Fem%3E%20before%20being%20put%20to%20use%20on%20the%20Indian%20railways%20since%20%E2%80%9Cthose%20at%20the%20top%E2%80%9D%20claim%20that%20in%20a%20comfortable%20chamber%20the%20LP%20will%20fall%20asleep.%20In%20a%202010%20study%20conducted%20by%20a%20team%20of%20railway%20doctors%20quoted%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Failrsa.com%2Fassets%2Fdocuments%2Fhpc_report_2.pdf%5C%22%3EHPC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20of%20100%20LPs%2C%2096%25%20identified%20%E2%80%9Cpostural%20discomfort%20and%20non-spacious%20work%20place%E2%80%9D%20and%2095%25%20%E2%80%9Cnoisy%20workplace%E2%80%9D%20as%20leading%20reasons%20for%20build-up%20of%20stress.%20These%20stresses%20and%20strains%20play%20out%20on%20the%20LPs%20body%20and%20mind%2C%20affecting%20his%2Fher%20concentration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESignal%20kahin%20bhi%20daal%20dete%20hai%20%E2%80%93%20pahaad%20pe%2C%20jhopdi%20pe%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWorking%20under%20these%20conditions%2C%20LPs%20claim%20that%20observing%20and%20complying%20with%20signals%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20difficult%20for%20them%20given%20the%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20signals%2C%20the%20flouting%20of%20signal%20placement%20norms%20and%20the%20dilapidation%20of%20the%20signalling%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20signals%20on%20railway%20routes%20has%20dramatically%20increased.%20For%20instance%2C%20LPs%20report%20that%20on%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20Terminus-Kalyan%20route%2C%20signals%2C%20which%20used%20to%20be%20at%20distances%20of%20two%20km%20from%20each%20other%2C%20are%20now%20at%20a%20stone%E2%80%99s%20throw%20from%20each%20other.%20So%2C%20in%20the%20journey%20from%20CST-Kalyan-CST%2C%20there%20are%20no%20less%20than%20400%20signals%20which%20the%20LP%20must%20observe%20and%20comply%20with.%20To%20take%20another%20example%2C%20on%20the%20Chennai%20Central-Vijayawada%20section%20of%20the%20Southern%20Railway%2C%20over%20430%20km%20there%20are%20386%20signals%2C%20i.e.%2C%20almost%20one%20per%20kilometre.%20On%20this%20route%20LPs%20on%20trains%20with%20speeds%20of%20120-130%20km%2Fhour%20encounter%20a%20signal%20every%2027%20seconds.%20While%20greater%20signalling%20is%20no%20doubt%20a%20positive%20development%2C%20for%20the%20overworked%20and%20under-slept%20LP%2C%20monitoring%20hundreds%20of%20signals%20causes%20continuous%20mental%20stress%2C%20and%20can%20only%20be%20effective%20if%20their%20working%20hours%20are%20reduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20stresses%20on%20the%20LP%20are%20increased%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20signal%20placement%20regulations%20are%20increasingly%20being%20flouted.%20Railway%20rules%20require%20that%20signals%20be%20placed%20uniformly%20at%20eye%20level%20on%20the%20left-hand%20side%20of%20the%20track%20it%20controls%2C%20or%20if%20there%20isn%E2%80%99t%20space%2C%20then%20above%20it.%20One%20can%20imagine%20that%20this%20regularity%20is%20essential%20for%20an%20LP%20to%20properly%20observe%20and%20comply%20with%20signals%20at%20speed%20for%20running%20times%20extending%20to%2011%20hours%20and%20more%2C%20particularly%20when%20their%20required%20area%20of%20observance%20and%20concentration%20keeps%20increasing%20with%20single%20line%20sections%20being%20converted%20to%20double%20and%20quadruple%20lines%20and%20the%20erection%20of%20overhead%20electrical%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20LPs%20claim%20that%20sub-contractors%20involved%20in%20signal%20construction%20have%20flouted%20rules%20regarding%20signal%20placement%2C%20sometimes%20putting%20signals%20on%20the%20right%20side%20of%20the%20track%20or%20at%20an%20elevation.%20An%20LP%20described%20the%20arbitrariness%20of%20signal%20placement%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20area%20this%20way%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESignal%20kahin%20bhi%20daal%20dete%20hai%20%E2%80%93%20pahaad%20pe%2C%20jhopdi%20pe%20%3C%2Fem%3E(The%20signal%20is%20placed%20just%20anywhere%20%E2%80%93%20on%20a%20mountain%2C%20on%20a%20hut).%E2%80%9D%20When%20signal%20placement%20is%20irregular%20and%20more%20than%20one%20track%20is%20running%20parallel%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20for%20LPs%20to%20know%20which%20signal%20is%20for%20their%20track%2C%20and%20which%20for%20the%20adjacent%20line.%20Moreover%2C%20in%20many%20places%2C%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fthe-nation%2Farticle30167487.ece%3Fart%3Dpackage%5C%22%3Eno%20arrow%20marks%3C%2Fa%3E%20pointing%20to%20the%20signal%2C%20which%20further%20confuses%20the%20LP%20in%20a%20situation%20which%20requires%20quick%20reactions.%20These%20factors%20greatly%20increase%20the%20possibility%20of%20LPs%20not%20being%20able%20to%20comply%20with%20signals%20on%20time%2C%20a%20situation%20which%20is%20known%20as%20%E2%80%9CSignal%20Passed%20At%20Danger%E2%80%9D%20(SPAD).%20Indeed%2C%20on%20August%2031%20on%20the%20above%20mentioned%20CST-Kalyan%20line%2C%20two%20local%20trains%20nearly%20collided%2C%20with%20Railway%20officials%20claiming%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mid-day.com%2Fmumbai%2Fmumbai-news%2Farticle%2Fmumbai-two-central-railway-local-trains-near-miss-head-on-collision-at-csmt-23306599%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cthe%20incorrect%20positioning%20of%20a%20signal%20post%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20might%20have%20led%20to%20the%20incident.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20to%20say%20nothing%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20in%202017%20there%20was%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fthe-nation%2Fodisha-train-accident-deaths-where-does-the-buck-stop%2Farticle66953983.ece%5C%22%3Eeight-year%20backlog%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20replacing%20signal%20gears%2C%20creating%20a%20situation%20where%20many%20small%20signal%20failures%20take%20place%20regularly%20on%20the%20network.%20Indeed%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcover-your-tracks-the-modi-governments-attitude-after-the-balasore-tragedy%5C%22%3EV.%20Sridhar%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20shown%2C%20a%20third%20of%20accidents%20due%20to%20equipment%20failure%20in%202021-22%20were%20the%20result%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfailure%20of%20signal%20apparatus%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20there%20are%20currently%2014%2C850%20vacancies%20in%20the%20Signalling%20Department%20of%20the%20Indian%20Railways.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYet%20despite%20these%20problems%20which%20do%20not%20allow%20them%20to%20attain%20proper%20speed%2C%20LPs%20claim%20they%20are%20fined%20and%20penalised%20by%20the%20railway%20administration%20if%20they%20arrive%20late%20at%20their%20destination.%20This%20pushes%20them%20to%20compromise%20on%20caution.%20One%20driver%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20lose%20our%20minds%20%E2%80%93%20if%20I%20have%20a%20yellow%20signal%20how%20can%20I%20go%20faster%3F%20But%20if%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20be%20penalised%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20toll%20it%20takes%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ERetirement%20ke%20pehle%20hi%20khatam%20ho%20jaate%20hain%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20all%20of%20this%2C%20goods%20LPs%20must%20also%20go%20through%20the%20traumatic%20experience%20of%20recovering%20and%20moving%20corpses%20from%20the%20tracks.%20When%20trains%20are%20running%20at%20high%20speeds%20animals%20and%20human%20beings%20trespassing%20on%20the%20tracks%20are%20sometimes%20unavoidably%20run%20over.%20When%20this%20happens%2C%20goods%20LPs%20must%2C%20along%20with%20guards%2C%20stop%20the%20train%20and%20clear%20the%20tracks%20of%20the%20corpse%2C%20which%20is%20often%20cut%20into%20pieces%20%E2%80%93%20a%20highly%20traumatic%20event.%20Yet%2C%20LPs%20claim%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20does%20not%20provide%20them%20with%20the%20necessary%20safety%20equipment%20to%20do%20this%20%E2%80%93%20not%20even%20gloves.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%202010%20study%20by%20Railway%20Doctors%20quoted%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Failrsa.com%2Fassets%2Fdocuments%2Fhpc_report_2.pdf%5C%22%3EHPC%3C%2Fa%3E%20cited%20earlier%20found%20that%20the%20various%20stressors%20in%20an%20LP%E2%80%99s%20work%20produce%20%E2%80%9Cdisrupted%20sexual%20functions%E2%80%9D%2C%20muscle%20aches%20and%20pains%2C%20sleep%20disturbances%2C%20headaches%2C%20stomach%20problems%2C%20%E2%80%9Cirritability%20and%20anger%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Cfrustration%20and%20anxiety%E2%80%9D.%20Many%20LPs%20also%20speak%20of%20blood%20pressure%20issues%20and%20diabetes%20being%20endemic%20among%20LPs.%20Due%20to%20the%20shortage%20of%20breaks%2C%20their%20family%20and%20social%20time%20is%20non-existent%2C%20which%20could%20help%20them%20deal%20with%20stress.%20One%20dejected%20LP%20replied%20when%20I%20asked%20about%20the%20life%20expectancy%20of%20LPs%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ERetirement%20ke%20pehle%20hi%20khatam%20ho%20jaate%20hain%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Death%20comes%20before%20retirement).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20these%20problems%2C%20rail%20accidents%20are%20blamed%20on%20the%20LP.%20But%20it%20stands%20to%20reason%20that%20the%20opposite%20is%20true.%20Given%20these%20conditions%2C%20it%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20abilities%20of%20LPs%20and%20their%20concern%20for%20safety%20that%20%3Cem%3Emore%3C%2Fem%3E%20accidents%20do%20not%20happen.%20It%20would%20be%20more%20accurate%20to%20say%20that%20railway%20workers%20are%20in%20fact%20keeping%20the%20railways%20safe%20%3Cem%3Edespite%3C%2Fem%3E%20their%20hours%20and%20conditions%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20working%20hours%20and%20conditions%20take%20their%20toll.%20As%20this%20article%20reached%20completion%2C%20CSMT%20ALP%20Sujit%20Jayant%20reportedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faifap.org.in%2F10086%2F%5C%22%3Edied%20by%20suicide%20at%20Kalyan%20on%20August%2014%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20the%20immediate%20issue%20was%20reported%20harassment%20by%20railway%20officials%20who%20were%20forcibly%20excluding%20him%20from%20work%20till%20September%2C%20LRSA%20officials%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faifap.org.in%2F10136%2F%5C%22%3Epointed%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20conditions%20of%20an%20LPs%20life%20and%20work%20were%20also%20a%20contributory%20factor.%20As%20a%20crowd%20of%20LPs%20gathered%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20harassment%20which%20led%20to%20Jayant%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FR80RohQuDNU%3Ft%3D41%5C%22%3Eprotested%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20use%20of%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9Csuicide%E2%80%9D%20to%20describe%20it.%20They%20insisted%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EMurder%20hua%20hai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(This%20was%20a%20murder).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EZaen%20Alkazi%20is%20a%20labour%20historian%20and%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695720653000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25132053%2F288A2183.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fpushed-to-the-limit-poor-stressful-work-conditions-mar-freight-train-drivers-lives%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Much%20of%20the%20work%20of%20checking%20of%20trains%20before%20departure%20has%20been%20put%20onto%20the%20shoulders%20of%20loco%20pilots%20and%20guards%20%E2%80%93%20a%20technical%20task%20they%20are%20not%20trained%20to%20do.%20Slackened%20safety%20standards%20are%20among%20the%20many%20troubles%20they%20face.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fpushed-to-the-limit-poor-stressful-work-conditions-mar-freight-train-drivers-lives%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zoleka%20Mandela%3A%20Nelson%20Mandela's%20granddaughter%20dies%20in%20South%20Africa%20at%2043%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695720456000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F5CB7%2Fproduction%2F_131253732_p04jvbdz.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-66921654%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She%20was%20well%20known%20for%20detailing%20her%20cancer%20treatment%20and%20being%20open%20about%20her%20past%20drug%20addiction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A173%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-66921654%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk