ent%20abides%20by%20the%20CWMA%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftamil-nadu-seeking-centres-support-to-settle-cauvery-dispute-dmk-leader-tiruchi-siva-4420427%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Seeking%20Centre's%20Support%20To%20Settle%20Cauvery%20Dispute%3A%20DMK%20Leader%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3EPolitical%20Row%20Over%20Cauvery%20Water-Sharing%20Order%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EPredictably%2C%20the%20opposition%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20-%20who%20this%20week%20announced%20an%20alliance%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20-%20have%20jumped%20in%20too%20and%20slammed%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20for%20having%20failed%20to%20protect%20the%20interests%20of%20farmers%20and%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-government-failed-to-convince-hd-kumaraswamy-on-cauvery-row-4418276%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BKarnataka%20Government%20Failed%20To%20Convince...%26quot%3B%3A%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20On%20Cauvery%20Row%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20said%20it%20is%20acting%20in%20the%20farmers'%20interest%2C%20and%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20has%20called%20for%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3ECauvery%20Water-Sharing%20History%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20battle%20that%20has%20raged%20for%20over%20a%20century%20should%20have%20concluded%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%202018%20order%2C%20which%20specified%20how%20much%20each%20party%20(including%20the%20city%20of%20Bengaluru%2C%20Kerala%20and%20Puducherry)%20should%20get%20from%20the%20Cauvery.%20The%20court's%20order%20was%20a%20revision%20of%20the%202007%20order%20passed%20by%20a%20tribunal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20never%20been%20that%20simple%20though%2C%20with%20Karnataka%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20frequently%20accusing%20the%20other%20of%20demanding%20too%20much%20and%20sharing%20too%20little%2C%20respectively.%20One%20problem%20is%20lack%20of%20clarity%20over%20water-sharing%20in%20a%20'distress%20year'%2C%20or%20a%20year%20in%20which%20there%20has%20been%20less-than-normal%20rainfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20dispute%20dates%20back%20to%20the%20colonial%20period.%20In%20a%201924%20agreement%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Puducherry%20were%20to%20get%20the%20lion's%20share%20of%20surplus%20water%20from%20the%20to-be-built%20Krishna%20Raja%20Sagar%20dam.%20Less%20than%20three%20decades%20later%20there%20was%20trouble%20again%2C%20including%20violent%20clashes%20over%20the%20construction%20of%20more%20dams.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20possibly%20when%20the%20water-sharing%20dispute%20really%20took%20off%2C%20as%20Tamil%20Nadu%20is%20a%20lower%20riparian%20state%20and%20was%2C%20by%20then%2C%20dependent%20on%20water%20from%20the%20Cauvery%20to%20water%20its%20crops.%20A%20proposal%20for%20Karnataka%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20each%20share%2047%20per%20cent%20of%20total%20water%20was%20refused%20by%20the%20latter%20state%20and%2C%20in%201986%2C%20the%20matter%20reached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20ordered%20a%20tribunal%20to%20settle%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fciqj2r28_bengaluru-protest-cauvery-1200_625x300_25_September_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tribunal%20gave%20Tamil%20Nadu%20205%20tmcft%20but%20that%20prompted%20protests%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20forcing%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20overrule%20the%20latter%20state's%20attempts%20to%20circumvent%20the%20order.%20In%201998%20a%20second%20tribunal%20was%20set%20up%20and%2C%20nine%20exhausting%20years%20later%2C%20reduced%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20share%20to%20192%20tmcft.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20water-sharing%20in%20a%20'distress%20year'%20was%20not%20specified.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20involved%20again%20in%202018%2C%20when%20it%20tweaked%20allocations.%20So%2C%20now%20Tamil%20Nadu%20is%20due%20404.25%20tmcft%2C%20or%20thousand%20million%20cubic%20feet%2C%20and%20Karnataka%20is%20to%20get%20284.75%20tmcft.%20The%20court%20also%20laid%20down%20rules%20to%20govern%20when%20water%20must%20be%20released%20and%20how%20much%20on%20each%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20groups%20are%20now%20again%20protesting%20this%20division%2C%20pointing%20to%20weather%20reports%20that%20say%20the%20region%20from%20which%20the%20Cauvery%20springs%20from%20had%20nearly%2030%20per%20cent%20deficit%20rainfall%2C%20while%20other%20catchment%20areas%20had%20nearly%2060%20per%20cent%20less%20rain%20than%20normal.%20This%2C%20they%20have%20stressed%2C%20means%20the%20state%20is%20simply%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20share%20water%20per%20normal%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695719940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-09%2Fm8qt98pg_cauvery-basin_625x300_29_September_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcauvery-water-sharing-explained-tamil-nadu-karnataka-fight-over-cauvery-water-again-what-is-the-dispute-4424725%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court's%20refusal%20to%20interfere%20with%20an%20order%20telling%20Karnataka%20to%20release%205%2C000%20cusecs%20of%20water%20daily%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%20for%2015%20days%20has%20sparked%20protests%20in%20the%20former%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcauvery-water-sharing-explained-tamil-nadu-karnataka-fight-over-cauvery-water-again-what-is-the-dispute-4424725%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcauvery-water-sharing-explained-tamil-nadu-karnataka-fight-over-