20a%20role%20in%20the%20selection%20of%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20in%20October%202015%20struck%20down%20the%20National%20Judicial%20Appointments%20Act%20that%20gave%20the%20bigger%20role%20of%20Executive%20in%20judges%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tussle%20between%20the%20Executive%20and%20Judiciary%20was%20raked%20up%20last%20year%20by%20Vice-President%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar's%20remarks%20on%20how%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20had%20%26quot%3Bundone%26quot%3B%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20the%20court%20had%20said%20the%20Collegium%20system%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Blaw%20of%20the%20land%26quot%3B%20which%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Bfollowed%20to%20the%20teeth%26quot%3B.%20Just%20because%20some%20sections%20of%20the%20society%20express%20a%20view%20against%20the%20Collegium%20system%2C%20it%20will%20not%20cease%20to%20be%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Collegium%20system%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20and%20seniormost%20judges%20recommend%20names%20of%20judges%20for%20appointment%20to%20high%20courts%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20names%20are%20sent%20to%20the%20centre%20and%20following%20its%20clearance%2C%20appointments%20are%20made%20by%20the%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695716280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-collegium-justice-sanjay-kishan-kaul-lots-to-say-but-supreme-courts-tough-talk-on-judges-appointments-4424552%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20what%20could%20turn%20into%20another%20faceoff%20between%20the%20Executive%20and%20Judiciary%20over%20judges'%20appointments%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20questioned%20why%2070%20recommendations%20of%20high%20courts%20have%20not%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20Collegium%20for%20consideration.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22