author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A54%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66921562%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66921562.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66921562.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Death%20row%20inmate%20fights%20being%20executed%20with%20nitrogen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695715320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F70x70%2Fskynews-kenneth-smith-alabama_6298379.jpg%3F20230926092928%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fdeath-row-inmate-fights-being-test-subject-for-new-execution-method-12970173%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20death%20row%20prisoner%20in%20Alabama%20is%20fighting%20plans%20for%20him%20to%20be%20the%20first%20person%20to%20be%20executed%20using%20nitrogen%20gas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fdeath-row-inmate-fights-being-test-subject-for-new-execution-method-12970173%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sikh%20Body%20Passes%20Resolution%20Asking%20India%2C%20Canada%20to%20Probe%20Allegations%20Amicably%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26132906%2FF639iptXEAAc0hz.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJalandhar%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Shiromani%20Gurdwara%20Parbandhak%20Committee%20(SGPC)%2C%20the%20apex%20body%20of%20Sikhs%20in%20India%2C%20on%20Monday%20(September%2025)%20expressed%20serious%20concern%20over%20the%20ongoing%20India-Canada%20diplomatic%20row%20and%20said%20that%20the%20statement%20of%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20parliament%20cannot%20be%20understood%20as%20%E2%80%9Ccommon%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20both%20countries%20should%20find%20ways%20to%20probe%20the%20allegations%20amicably.%20The%20statement%20indicates%20the%20sentiment%20among%20SGPC%20members%20that%20the%20Indian%20side%20may%20have%20handled%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20irresponsibly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExpressing%20concern%20over%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20of%20the%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20agencies%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20pro-Khalistani%20activist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20the%20SGPC%20in%20its%20executive%20meeting%20passed%20a%20special%20resolution%20on%20the%20ongoing%20India-Canada%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20special%20resolution%2C%20SGPC%20president%20Harjinder%20Singh%20Dhami%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CEverything%20said%20by%20PM%20Justin%20Trudeau%20in%20the%20Canadian%20parliament%20cannot%20be%20rejected%20easily.%20%E2%80%A6a%20sincere%20approach%20should%20be%20followed%20by%20both%20the%20countries%20to%20sort%20out%20this%20matter.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDhami%20said%20that%20if%20this%20case%20was%20suppressed%20only%20because%20of%20politics%2C%20it%20would%20be%20considered%20as%20injustice%20to%20human%20rights.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20truth%20of%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20the%20%5BCanadian%5D%20PM%20against%20the%20Indian%20agencies%20should%20be%20brought%20to%20light%20before%20the%20public%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20strongly%20condemned%20the%20propaganda%20being%20spread%20by%20the%20mainstream%20media%20and%20various%20social%20media%20platforms%20against%20Sikhs%20and%20the%20state%20of%20Punjab.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20observed%20that%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20India-Canada%20standoff%2C%20the%20mainstream%20media%20was%20deliberately%20indulging%20in%20the%20character%20assassination%20of%20the%20Sikhs.%20We%20demand%20serious%20action%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20against%20those%20who%20are%20tarnishing%20the%20image%20of%20the%20Sikh%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20resolution%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20SGPC%E2%80%99s%20special%20resolution%2C%20former%20president%20of%20the%20SGPC%20and%20its%20first%20ever%20woman%20chief%2C%20Bibi%20Jagir%20Kaur%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Punjabis%E2%80%99%20stakes%20were%20high%20in%20Canada.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20lakhs%20of%20Punjabis%20are%20settled%20in%20Canada%2C%20any%20further%20deterioration%20of%20India-Canada%20relations%20would%20adversely%20affect%20both%20the%20countries.%20It%20is%20the%20common%20Punjabis%2C%20the%20students%2C%20working%20class%20and%20the%20elderly%20in%20Canada%2C%20who%20would%20face%20trouble%20if%20the%20India-Canada%20standoff%20does%20not%20come%20to%20an%20end%20soon.%20India%20and%20Canada%20should%20seriously%20think%20over%20this%20diplomatic%20row%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKaur%20said%20that%20every%20Sikh%20was%20not%20a%20Khalistani%20or%20a%20terrorist.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20actions%20of%20a%20few%20cannot%20define%20the%20entire%20Sikh%20community.%20No%20Sikh%20or%20for%20that%20matter%20a%20Punjabi%20would%20ever%20indulge%20in%20humiliating%20or%20defaming%20any%20community.%20The%20Indian%20government%20should%20rein%20in%20the%20loud%20mouth%20and%20inflammatory%20mainstream%20media%2C%20as%20many%20were%20hurting%20the%20sentiments%20of%20Sikhs.%20We%20welcome%20fact-based%20news%20but%20mainstream%20news%20channels%20are%20crossing%20the%20line%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20does%20not%20belong%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20alone%2C%20it%20belongs%20to%20everybody%2C%20she%20continued.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20feel%20equally%20concerned%20over%20allegations%20against%20the%20Sikh%20community%20and%20terming%20them%20as%20Khalistanis.%20The%20Indian%20government%20should%20understand%20that%20such%20actions%20would%20lead%20to%20mistrust%20in%20the%20government.%20The%20Modi%20government%20should%20assure%20people%20that%20they%20are%20for%20the%20public%20and%20not%20against%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20on%20the%20reports%20of%20some%20people%20trying%20to%20create%20a%20divide%20by%20intimidating%20Hindus%20in%20Canada%2C%20SGPC%20chief%20Dhami%20clarified%20that%20the%20Sikh%20community%20respects%20all%20religions%20and%20does%20not%20hold%20enmity%20against%20anyone.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20people%20were%20using%20the%20current%20situation%20as%20a%20weapon%20to%20create%20divisions%20among%20communities%2C%20which%20should%20be%20stopped%20immediately.%20The%20Central%20government%20should%20look%20into%20this%20matter.%20Appropriate%20steps%20should%20be%20taken%20to%20end%20the%20growing%20mistrust%20among%20the%20Sikhs%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20SGPC%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBibi%20Kiranjot%20Kaur%2C%20the%20granddaughter%20of%20Master%20Tara%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20one%20of%20the%20founder%20members%20of%20the%20SGPC%2C%20said%20that%20India%20has%20handled%20the%20India-Canada%E2%80%99s%20diplomatic%20row%20irresponsibly%20and%20immaturely.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20fact%20is%20that%20most%20Sikhs%20left%20for%20Canada%20post%20Operation%20Bluestar%20and%20during%20militancy%20to%20save%20their%20lives.%20Following%20the%20India-Canada%20row%2C%20the%20general%20sentiment%20among%20Sikhs%20in%20Canada%20is%20that%20if%20they%20are%20not%20safe%20even%20after%20leaving%20Punjab%2C%20then%20where%20could%20they%20consider%20themselves%20as%20safe%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20if%20the%20Indian%20government%20stops%20giving%20hype%20to%20US-based%20Sikhs%20for%20Justice%20leader%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannu%2C%20his%20identity%20in%20Punjab%20and%20across%20the%20world%20would%20be%20that%20of%20a%20nobody.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKiranjot%20Kaur%20also%20said%20everybody%20talks%20about%20Operation%20Bluestar%20but%20nobody%20talks%20about%20Operation%20Woodrose%2C%20when%20the%20Army%2C%20police%20and%20the%20CRPF%20cracked%20down%20on%20every%20single%20house%20and%20village%20in%20Punjab%20during%20militancy.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20picked%20up%20young%20college%20and%20school%20going%20boys.%20If%20the%20Indian%20mainstream%20media%20was%20raking%20up%20the%20Khalistani%20narrative%2C%20it%20was%20because%20the%20Modi%20government%20was%20agreeing%20to%20it.%20Also%2C%20the%20mainstream%20media%20connects%20the%20demand%20of%20Khalistan%20with%20Jarnail%20Singh%20Bhindrawale%20but%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20he%20never%20even%20demanded%20it.%20It%20is%20the%20Indian%20government%20and%20its%20%E2%80%98keyboard%20warriors%E2%80%99%2C%20who%20are%20building%20this%20narrative%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20SGPC%20member%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20when%20a%20crime%20takes%20place%20in%20other%20states%2C%20the%20accused%20are%20termed%20as%20%E2%80%98gangsters%E2%80%99%20but%20in%20case%20of%20Punjab%2C%20they%20are%20directly%20called%20%E2%80%98Khalistanis%E2%80%99.%20%E2%80%9CThen%20the%20Modi%20government%20says%20that%20they%20face%20resistance%20in%20Punjab.%20If%20the%20government%20will%20continue%20with%20the%20policy%20of%20repression%2C%20they%20will%20face%20resistance%20from%20Punjab%20and%20Sikhs%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20SGPC%20member%2C%20Kulwant%20Singh%20Mannan%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20in%20Vancouver%2C%20said%20that%20contrary%20to%20reports%20fuelling%20confusion%20and%20fear%2C%20everything%20was%20normal%20in%20Canada.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20were%20busy%20in%20their%20jobs%20and%20there%20is%20absolutely%20no%20threat%20to%20any%20community%2C%20particularly%20the%20Hindus.%20There%20is%20no%20such%20issue%20in%20Canada.%20All%20communities%20whether%20Sikhs%20or%20Hindus%20are%20living%20in%20harmony.%20It%20is%20highly%20unfortunate%20and%20deeply%20worrying%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20mainstream%20TV%20news%20channels%20are%20creating%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20fear%20everywhere%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20diplomatic%20row%2C%20Mannan%20said%20that%20Trudeau%20spoke%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20as%20a%20Canadian%20citizen.%20%E2%80%9CLet%20us%20not%20forget%20that%20India%20and%20Canada%20have%20always%20shared%20friendly%20relations.%20Canada%20has%20elevated%20the%20lives%20of%20people%20who%20moved%20there%20from%20Punjab.%20It%20is%20very%20important%20that%20both%20nations%20tackle%20this%20matter%20sensitively%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20SGPC%20also%20held%20an%20online%20meeting%20of%20the%20International%20Sikh%20Advisory%20Board%20constituted%20by%20the%20SGPC%20in%20which%20representatives%20from%20the%20US%2C%20UK%20and%20Canada%20participated.%20The%20meeting%20assumed%20significance%20as%20it%20took%20place%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20India-Canada%20standoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20global%20concerns%20of%20the%20Sikh%20community%20were%20discussed.%20Bhai%20Mohinder%20Singh%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Guru%20Nanak%20Nishkam%20Seva%20Jatha%20UK%2C%20and%20Bibi%20Inderjit%20Kaur%20of%20Sikh%20Dharma%20International%20US%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20special%20efforts%20to%20organise%20Sikhs%20across%20the%20entire%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20discussed%20that%20every%20Gurdwara%20in%20the%20world%20should%20be%20associated%20with%20Sri%20Akal%20Takht%20Sahib%20and%20an%20agenda%20should%20be%20prepared%20for%20the%20needs%2C%20problems%20and%20tasks%20of%20Sikhs%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20global%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESGPC%20president%20Harjinder%20Singh%20Dhami%2C%20who%20led%20this%20meeting%2C%20said%20that%20the%20International%20Sikh%20Advisory%20Board%20was%20constituted%20to%20address%20the%20global%20affairs%20of%20Sikhs%2C%20and%20its%20meetings%20would%20continue%20and%20suggestions%20received%20will%20be%20considered.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695715230000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26132906%2FF639iptXEAAc0hz.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ft