0that%20China%20will%20not%20go%20to%20war%20with%20India%20because%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20says%20this%20is%20%E2%80%98not%20an%20era%20of%20war.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENothing%20can%20be%20hollower%20than%20a%20military%20which%20believes%20its%20own%20propaganda.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EPravin%20Sawhney%E2%80%99s%20recent%20book%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Last%20War%3A%20How%20AI%20Will%20Shape%20India%E2%80%99s%20Final%20Showdown%20With%20China%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695709822000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F18143010%2FIMG_0265.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fpoliticising-the-armed-forces-has-consequences%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Anantnag%20tragedy%20was%20waiting%20to%20happen%20because%20the%20Indian%20Army%20may%20have%20started%20believing%20the%20BJP%20government%20propaganda%20that%20the%20revocation%20of%20Article%20370%20had%20resolved%20the%20Kashmir%20issue.%20It%20started%20believing%20the%20crude%20sloganeering%20by%20retired%20army%20officers%20claiming%20that%20Pakistan%20is%20a%20walkover.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fpoliticising-the-armed-forces-has-consequences%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Crocodile%20expert%20admits%20sexually%20abusing%20and%20killing%20dogs%20-%20as%20judge%20warns%20details%20could%20cause%20'nervous%20shock'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695709260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F70x70%2Fskynews-adam-britton-zoologist_6298248.jpg%3F20230926072741%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fsadistic-british-crocodile-expert-adam-brit