lUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fnorth-korea-nukes-kim-jong-un-south-korea-warning%2Farticleshow%2F103949634.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fnorth-korea-nukes-kim-jong-un-south-korea-warning%2Famp_articleshow%2F103949634.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fnorth-korea-nukes-kim-jong-un-south-korea-warning%2Famp_articleshow%2F103949634.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Is%20in%20a%20Sugary%20Mess%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26103523%2Fsugar-485055_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20battling%20months%20of%20hyper-food%20inflation%20of%20vegetables%20like%20tomatoes%20and%20onion%2C%20legumes%2C%20rice%2C%20etc.%2C%20India%20is%20faced%20with%20another%20food%20problem%20%E2%80%93%20sugar.%20The%20low%20rainfall%20in%20August%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20sugar-growing%20areas%2C%20resulted%20in%20a%20drought-like%20condition%20and%20the%20government%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fmaryroeloffs%2F2023%2F08%2F23%2Findia-to-ban-sugar-exports-in-addition-to-rice-as-corn-soybeans-and-more-crops-falter-in-extreme-heat-and-drought%2F%3Fsh%3D4877b64a6d6c%5C%22%3Eban%20sugar%20exports%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Findia-set-ban-sugar-exports-first-time-7-years-2023-08-23%2F%3Ftaid%3D64e5fbc9c89a480001599a2b%5C%22%3Efirst%20time%20in%20seven%20years%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Major%20producing%20states%20like%20Maharashtra%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Fsugar-output-indias-maharashtra-set-fall-lowest-4-yrs-after-dry-august-2023-09-13%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%20a%2014%25%20drop%3C%2Fa%3E%20(lowest%20in%20four%20years)%20in%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWorld%20over%2C%20sugar%20experts%20were%20watching%20the%20Indian%20monsoon%20and%20Cyclone%20Biparjoy.%20As%20it%20was%20destroying%20Kharif%20sowing%2C%20speculators%20around%20the%20world%20were%20hedging%20on%20sugar%20prices.%20That%20India%20may%20ban%20sugar%20exports%20only%20added%20to%20their%20fortunes%2C%20as%20sugar%20prices%20had%20already%20jumped%2030%25%20from%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20the%20global%20market%20better%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20look%20at%20another%20major%20producer%20%E2%80%93%20Brazil.%20The%20United%20States%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fas.usda.gov%2Fdata%2Fbrazil-sugar-annual-9%5C%22%3Erecently%20predicted%20a%206.5%25%20increase%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20production%20due%20to%20favourable%20weather%20and%20higher%20sugar%20prices%2C%20but%20it%20is%20uncertain%20how%20much%20actual%20sugar%20will%20reach%20the%20international%20market%20as%20Brazil%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Fbrazil-mills-cancel-sugar-export-contracts-shift-output-ethanol-2022-05-17%2F%5C%22%3Ediverts%20its%20surplus%20sugar%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20bio-fuel%20and%20ethanol.%20Brazil%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20the%20Global%20Biofuel%20Alliance%20started%20at%20the%20G20%20in%20New%20Delhi%20also%20signals%20that%20Brazil%20is%20not%20leaving%20her%20bio-fuel%20industry%20on%20the%20simmer%20any%20time%20soon.%20Especially%20as%20Brazil%E2%80%99s%20sugar%20and%20bio-fuel%20industry%20are%20deeply%20tied%20to%20the%20US.%20Brazil%20is%20the%20second-largest%20recipient%20of%20the%20US%20sugar%20tariff-rate%20quota%20with%20an%20allocation%20for%20%E2%80%9CFY%202023%20TRQ%20of%20196%2C440%20metric%20tons%2C%20raw%20value%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20its%20usual%20international%20customers%2C%20Brazil%20also%20exported%20its%20raw%20sugar%20to%20Russia%2C%20Iran%20and%20other%20African%20countries.%20The%20Indian%20sugar%20export%20ban%20creates%20a%20big%20opportunity%20for%20Brazil%20to%20keep%20her%20farmers%20happy.%20Keep%20in%20mind%2C%20Thailand%20has%20also%20had%20bad%20year%20and%20there%20will%20be%20additional%20demand%20for%20Brazilian%20sugar%20from%20many%20Indian%20buyers%20too%2C%20if%20the%20prices%20are%20not%20checked.%20With%20limited%20supply%2C%20the%20sugar%20market%20may%20very%20well%20be%20a%20sellers%E2%80%99%20and%20commodity%20traders%E2%80%99%20dream%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndian%20sugar%20ban%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20the%20public%20panic%20over%20sugar%20began%2C%20policymakers%20were%20quick%20to%20ban%20the%20export%20of%20the%20sugar%20because%20the%20Indian%20government%20cannot%20afford%20further%20food%20price%20inflation.%20Branching%20off%20to%20understand%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20knee-jerk%20policy%2C%20let%20us%20see%20the%20tomato%20crisis.%20The%20remedy%20measures%20for%20stabilising%20the%20tomato%2C%20onion%20and%20vegetable%20fiasco%20already%20shed%20a%20bad%20light%20on%20agrarian%20policy%20and%20state%20efficiency.%20Loss%20of%20forex%20is%20an%20additional%20burden.%20The%20result%20was%20that%20prices%20stabilised%20after%20a%20few%20months%2C%20but%20with%20the%20new%20harvest%20of%20tomatoes%2C%20prices%20have%20crashed%20for%20farmers%20again.%20Reportedly%20farmers%20are%20once%20again%20only%20receiving%20under%20Rs%204-5%2Fkg%20for%20their%20tomatoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20dare%20say%2C%20if%20such%20flip-flop%20happens%20with%20sugarcane%20farmers%20and%20the%20industry%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20disaster.%20Hence%20the%20government%20after%20the%20export%20ban%20also%20put%20additional%20measures.%20This%20time%20all%20stocking%20limits%20have%20to%20be%20declared%20by%20retailers%2C%20traders%2C%20big%20processors%2C%20whole%20sellers%2C%20etc.%20and%20all%20stock%20quantities%20have%20to%20reported%20to%20the%20government%20portal%20on%20a%20weekly%20basis%20every%20Monday.%20The%20government%20says%20that%20these%20steps%20are%20taken%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccombat%20hoarding%20and%20curb%20unscrupulous%20speculation%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20sugar%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%20this%20also%20presents%20two%20other%20problems%20%E2%80%93%20one%20electoral%20and%20the%20second%20agrarian%20cum%20international.%20We%20will%20begin%20with%20the%20latter.%20India%20led%20the%20Global%20Biofuel%20Alliance%20from%20the%20front.%20Whenever%20this%20Alliance%20becomes%20an%20incarnated%20entity%2C%20it%20would%20require%20India%20to%20have%20a%20healthy%20bio-fuel%20industry%20too.%20Without%20sufficient%20and%20cheap%20supply%20of%20raw%20material%20or%20sugar%2C%20it%20would%20be%20very%20hard%20to%20encourage%20the%20bio-fuel%20industry%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20government%20continues%20to%20oscillate%20between%20good%20and%20bad%20years%20on%20sugar%20policy%2C%20no%20serious%20players%20would%20be%20interested%20in%20investing%20in%20the%20market.%20What%20I%20mean%20by%20that%20is%20%E2%80%93%20imagine%20India%20has%20a%20mid-sized%20sugarcane%20based%20ethanol%20industry%20built%20upon%20raw%20material%20clusters%20in%20the%20country.%20Now%20like%202023%2C%20if%20again%20because%20of%20one%20or%20two%20bad%20rains%20the%20sugarcane%20production%20diminishes%20and%20the%20government%20bans%20sugarcane%20for%20ethanol%3F%20In%20all%20likelihood%2C%20whether%20BJP%20or%20Congress%2C%20they%20will%20follow%20the%20electorate%20logic%20and%20divert%20sugarcane%20for%20sugar%20before%20ethanol%20production.%20This%20will%20put%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20biofuel%20industry%2C%20like%20with%20the%20case%20of%20the%20sugar%20industry%2C%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20political%20masters.%20Sugar%20in%20India%20is%20also%20a%20very%20political%20crop%2C%20involving%20co-operatives%2C%20politicians%2C%20mills%2C%20industry%20and%20the%20government.%20And%20no%20new-age%20venture%20capitalist%20or%20fund%20will%20place%20money%20on%20a%20project%20contingent%20on%20political%20whims%2C%20especially%20when%20the%20production%20can%20dwindle%20any%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWithout%20stabilised%20sugarcane%20production%2C%20biofuel%20is%20an%20expensive%20and%20impractical%20dream.%20The%20current%20situation%20has%20exhibited%20this%20quite%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%20comes%20the%20electoral%20problem.%20The%20Indian%20consumers%20may%20get%20to%20the%20boiling%20point%2C%20because%20sugar%20is%20critical%20for%20the%20Indian%20thali.%20And%20more%20pressure%20to%20rob%20the%20thali%20of%20sugar%20may%20be%20perceived%20by%20electorate%20(including%20farmers)%20as%20a%20direct%20attack.%20And%20speaking%20of%20farmers%2C%20due%20to%20the%20hyper%20inflation%20%E2%80%93%20rising%20fuel%20to%20vegetables%20costs%2C%20dampened%20production%20and%20bad%20weather%2C%20rural%20India%20will%20demand%20higher%20MGNREGA%20rates%20and%20MSP.%20For%20sugarcane%2C%20the%20state%20sugarcane%20prices%20would%20have%20to%20be%20increased%20to%20please%20voters%20in%20these%20politically%20active%20regions%20adding%20to%20the%20sugar%20price%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20look%20of%20it%2C%20the%20government%20and%20people%20appear%20to%20be%20in%20a%20sugary%20mess.%20The%20government%20needs%20to%20tread%20very%20carefully%20if%20it%20wants%20to%20avoid%20a%20sugar%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndra%20Shekhar%20Singh%20is%20an%20independent%20agri-policy%20analyst%20and%20writer.%20He%20was%20the%20former%20director%2C%20policy%20and%20outreach%2C%20at%20NSAI.%20He%20also%20hosts%20The%20Wire%E2%80%99s%20agriculture%20talk%20show%2C%20Krishi%20ki%20baat%2FFarm%20Talks.%20He%20tweets%20%40indrassingh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695704958000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26103523%2Fsugar-485055_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Findia-is-in-a-sugary-mess%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20explains%20the%20gove