derstand%20what%20they%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20problem%20is%20that%20most%20people%20with%20dementia%20or%20children%20won%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20tracking%20devices%20on%20them%2C%20which%20makes%20things%20difficult.%20Speaking%20to%20the%20caregivers%2C%20I%20realised%20how%20stressed%20they%20get%20when%20their%20loved%20one%20walks%20off.%20I%20wanted%20to%20build%20something%20solid%20for%20them%2C%20which%20is%20a%20fool-proof%20way%20of%20finding%20their%20child%2C%20or%20parent%2C%20or%20spouse%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Akshay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20these%20people%20are%20also%20unable%20to%20communicate%20effectively.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20QR%20tags%20are%20an%20insurance%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Akshay.%20%E2%80%9CI%20created%20this%20mechanism%20so%20that%20the%20identification%20process%20is%20sped%20up%20and%20the%20missing%20citizens%20can%20come%20home%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20you%20need%20to%20do%20is%20log%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprojectchetna.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20click%20on%20register%2C%20fill%20in%20the%20personal%20details%20of%20the%20person%20you%E2%80%99re%20making%20it%20for%2C%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20get%20the%20QR%20pendant.%20Anyone%20with%20a%20phone%20can%20scan%20the%20code%20and%20get%20the%20information.%20Akshay%20is%20also%20building%20technology%20that%20will%20alert%20you%20when%20anyone%20scans%20the%20QR.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20if%20someone%20from%20Mumbai%20has%20wandered%20off%20to%20Bengaluru.%20If%20someone%20there%20scans%20the%20QR%2C%20you%20will%20get%20a%20notification.%20This%20will%20help%20save%20the%20lives%20of%20people%20who%20go%20missing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20need%20for%20empathy%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2