india.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-2-1695300985-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-2-1695300985-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-2-1695300985-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330489%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESonali%20was%20also%20a%20probationary%20trainee%20at%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%20in%20her%20early%20career%20days.%C2%A0Picture%20credit%3A%20Sonali%20Ghosh%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20on%20the%20situation%20then%2C%20she%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20express%20enough%20gratitude%20for%20my%20parents%E2%80%99%20unwavering%20support%20of%20my%20dreams.%20However%2C%20upon%20reflection%2C%20it%20becomes%20evident%20that%20it%20was%20societal%20norms%20that%20once%20impeded%20the%20progress%20of%20women%20like%20me.%20With%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20efforts%2C%20I%20never%20let%20the%20societal%20pressure%20win.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20similar%20lines%2C%20Sonali%20also%20recalled%20how%20being%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20highly%20male-dominated%20profession%20played%20out%20for%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20terms%20of%20mental%20well-being%2C%20workplaces%20in%20Assam%20and%20North%20Easter%20India%20are%20far%20better%20than%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%20Women%20are%20free%20to%20dress%2C%20talk%20and%20behave%20in%20any%20manner%20they%20wish%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20since%20the%20job%20was%20male-dominated%2C%20the%20workplace%20often%20lacked%20hygiene%20requirements%20for%20a%20woman%20worker.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLiving%20comfortably%20was%20very%20hard%20to%20come%20by%20back%20in%20those%20days.%20There%20was%20always%20a%20lack%20of%20hygiene%2C%20However%2C%20things%20have%20become%20much%20better%20with%20more%20women%20joining%20the%20workforce%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20she%20fared%20as%20the%20only%20woman%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20gender%20discrimination%20in%20the%20field%2C%20Ghosh%20recalls%20a%20time%20when%20she%20worked%20as%20a%20young%20ACF%20(Assistant%20Conservator%20of%20Forest)%20and%20was%20the%20only%20woman%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20around%20me%20would%20take%20some%20time%20to%20digest%20that%20a%20woman%20was%20in%20command.%20I%20would%20often%20hear%20gossip%20and%20chattering%20behind%20my%20back%2C%20but%20I%20never%20let%20it%20bother%20me.%20The%20one%20advice%20to%20all%20women%20out%20there%20in%20such%20a%20setting%20would%20be%20to%20develop%20a%20Rhino-like%20thick%20skin%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20general%2C%20the%20mindset%20of%20male%20bosses%20or%20colleagues%20is%20that%20women%20are%20meant%20for%20%E2%80%98softer%E2%80%99%20jobs.%20They%20thought%20that%20women%20could%20not%20or%20should%20not%20put%20in%20extra%20hours%20as%20they%20would%20need%20to%20tend%20to%20children%20and%20families.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we%20have%20had%20to%20work%20extra%20hard%20to%20prove%20ourselves.%20But%20our%20assertiveness%20or%20proactive%20behaviour%20is%20often%20misconstrued%20as%20aggression%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-3-1695301158.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sonali%20says%20that%20being%20in%20nature%20and%20among%20wildlife%20makes%20her%20job%20more%20fun%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-3-1695301158.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2