C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%20Ghosh's%20newfound%20responsibilities%20encompass%20patrolling%20and%20surveillance%20to%20thwart%20poachers%20and%20coming%20to%20the%20aid%20of%20wild%20animals%20in%20distress.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330492%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGhosh%E2%80%99s%20newfound%20responsibilities%20encompass%20patrolling%20and%20surveillance%20to%20thwart%20poachers%20and%20coming%20to%20the%20aid%20of%20wild%20animals%20in%20distress.%20Picture%20Credit%3A%20Sonali%20Ghosh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20role%20demands%20precise%20monitoring%20of%20wildlife%20through%20scientific%20techniques%20and%20the%20careful%20management%20of%20tourism%20through%20the%20creation%20and%20execution%20of%20ecotourism%20initiatives.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDescribing%20her%20work%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20and%20foremost%2C%20I%20need%20to%20be%20an%20effective%20listener%20and%20understand%20how%20this%20famed%20protected%20area%20works.%20I%20have%20a%20great%20team%20with%20one%20of%20the%20finest%20forest%20frontline-to-area%20ratios%20in%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20first%20priority%20would%20be%20to%20continue%20with%20its%20protection%2C%20ensure%20and%20strengthen%20Rhinoceros%20and%20other%20flagship%20species%E2%80%99%20conservation.%20The%20second%20priority%20would%20be%20the%20utmost%20welfare%20of%20the%20forest%20frontline%20staff%20who%20serve%2024%C3%977%20in%20one%20of%20the%20toughest%20conditions%20at%20Kaziranga%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20has%20only%20been%2020%20days%20since%20Sonali%20assumed%20the%20new%20responsibility%2C%20she%20is%20quite%20geared%20up%20for%20the%20upcoming%20workload.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20great%20responsibility%20and%20I%20am%20thankful%20to%20the%20state%20government%20for%20giving%20me%20the%20opportunity.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20wait%20to%20give%20my%20best%20to%20nature%20and%20conserve%20the%20wildlife%20of%20the%20national%20park%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20women%20aspiring%20to%20be%20in%20the%20field%20of%20forest%20and%20wildlife%20conservation%20in%20India%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWomen%20and%20young%20ladies%20who%20love%20outdoors%20and%20want%20to%20make%20a%20difference%2C%20be%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20communities%20must%20drop%20all%20their%20apprehensions%20and%20give%20it%20a%20try.%20There%20are%20several%20opportunities%20to%20explore%20and%20the%20sky%E2%80%99s%20the%20limit!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695303144000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330465%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sonali%20Ghosh%2C%20who%20assumed%20the%20role%20as%20the%20field%20director%20of%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%20on%201%20September%2C%202023%2C%20grew%20up%20having%20a%20close%20affinity%20to%20animals.%20By%20the%20time%20she%20completed%20her%20graduation%20in%20life%20sciences%2C%20her%20affinity%20had%20turned%20into%20a%20full%20blown%20passion.%20Being%20in%20forest%20and%20wildlife%20conservation%20for%20decades%2C%20she%20recalls%20the%20hurdles%2C%20challenges%20and%20offers%20a%20glimpse%20into%20her%20life%20now.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330465%2Ffirst-woman-director-of-kaziranga-national-park-struggles-challenges-stereotypes%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tripura%20IAS%20Officer%E2%80%99s%20Idea%20Is%20Preventing%20Girls%20From%20Leaving%20School%3B%20Stopped%2090%20Child%20Marriages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20on%20her%20way%20home%20from%20school%2C%2016-year-old%20Jyotsana%20Akhtar%20from%20Tripura%E2%80%99s%20Amzadnagar%20village%20heard%20people%20whispering%20while%20looking%20at%20her.%20When%20she%20overheard%20their%20conversation%2C%20she%20was%20taken%20aback%20to%20learn%20that%20her%20marriage%20was%20fixed!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20returned%20home%2C%20my%20%3Cem%3Ebaba%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Emaa%3C%2Fem%3E%20didn%E2%80%99t%20mention%20anything%20about%20the%20marriage.%20I%20found%20out%20from%20the%20villagers%20that%20I%20was%20to%20marry%20a%20man%20twice%20my%20age%20who%20had%20been%20divorced.%20It%20seemed%20like%20all%20my%20fears%20were%20soon%20to%20turn%20into%20reality%2C%20and%20I%20did%20not%20know%20if%20I%20would%20ever%20return%20to%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jyotsana%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20retaliated%20and%20refused%20to%20get%20married%20so%20early.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20study%20further%20and%20get%20a%20good%20job%2C%20if%20possible%20earn%20better%20than%20the%20man%20with%20whom%20my%20marriage%20was%20fixed.%20But%20my%20parents%20did%20not%20understand%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith